ment%20in%20the%20statement%20said%2C%20%26quot%3BThe%20Lahaina%20fire%20is%20not%20yet%20contained.%26quot%3B%20Earlier%2C%20Hawaii%20Governor%20Josh%20Green%20said%20that%20the%20death%20toll%20from%20the%20wildfires%20on%20the%20island%20of%20Maui%20in%20Hawaii%20reaches%2059.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESpeaking%20to%20CNN%2C%20Green%20said%20that%20all%20those%20deaths%20occurred%20in%20the%20open%20and%20not%20in%20buildings%2C%20%26quot%3Bas%20people%20were%20trying%20to%20escape%20the%20fire.%26quot%3B%20He%20said%20that%20there%20will%20be%20more%20fatalities.%20Josh%20Green%20said%2C%20%26quot%3BWithout%20a%20doubt%2C%20there%20will%20be%20more%20fatalities.%20We%20do%20not%20know%2C%20ultimately%2C%20how%20many%20will%20have%20occurred.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHawaii's%20Governor%20ordered%20a%20comprehensive%20review%20of%20the%20state's%20actions%20in%20the%20hours%20after%20the%20wildfires%20erupted%20on%20the%20islands%2C%20earlier%20this%20week%2C%20including%20why%20warning%20sirens%20were%20not%20utilised%20to%20alert%20people%20on%20Maui.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESpeaking%20to%20CNN%2C%20Green%20said%2C%20%26quot%3BI%20authorized%20a%20comprehensive%20review%20this%20morning%2C%20to%20make%20sure%20that%20we%20know%20exactly%20what%20happened%20and%20when.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHe%20said%20that%20the%20emergency%20officials%20particularly%20faced%20challenges%20as%20the%20flames%20burning%20near%20Lahaina%2C%20which%20ultimately%20turned%20into%20a%20firestorm%20that%20razed%20nearly%20all%20of%20the%20historic%20town%20had%20died%20down%20for%20sometime%20before%20suddenly%20reigniting%2C%20and%20firefighters%20had%20shifted%20their%20focus%20to%20other%20areas%20on%20the%20island.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThe%20telecommunications%20were%20destroyed%20very%20rapidly%26quot%3B%20at%20that%20point%2C%20Green%20said%2C%20meaning%20that%20the%20tight-knit%20community%20was%20unable%20to%20alert%20one%20another%20by%20phone%2C%20as%20they%20typi