ression%20that%20we%20will%20get%20an%20autonomous%20territorial%20council%20under%20the%20Sixth%20Schedule%2C%20like%20the%20Bodos%20of%20Assam%20have%2C%20which%20would%20have%20been%20a%20significant%20win%20for%20our%20political%20movement.%20With%20financial%20independence%20from%20the%20state%20government%20in%20Imphal%2C%20it%20would%20have%20been%20almost%20like%20having%20a%20separate%20state%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20told%C2%A0%3Cem%3EThe%20Wire%3C%2Fem%3E.%C2%A0The%20insurgent%20leader%2C%C2%A0however%2C%20added%2C%20%E2%80%9CPost%20May%203%20violence%20though%2C%20there%20is%20a%20strong%20public%20demand%20for%20a%20separate%20state%2C%20not%20territorial%20council%2C%20and%2C%20therefore%2C%20our%20stand%20is%20also%20changing.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EBiren%C2%A0Singh%20not%20in%20support%3F%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Union%20government%20led%20by%20the%20BJP%20was%20in%20favour%20of%20signing%20a%20peace%20treaty%20with%20the%20Kuki%20SoO%20groups%20on%20May%208%2C%20but%20the%20Manipur%20government%20led%20by%20chief%20minister%20N%20Biren%20Singh%20was%20not%20and%20he%20made%20that%20amply%20clear%2C%20it%20is%20learnt.%20He%20%E2%80%9Chad%20got%20a%20wind%20of%20it%20and%20was%20extremely%20unhappy%3B%20he%20was%20sending%20us%20feelers%20through%20various%20channels%20not%20to%20go%20ahead%20with%20it%2C%E2%80%9D%20sources%20confirmed%20to%20%3Cem%3EThe%20Wire.%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESeveral%20Meitei%20civil%20society%C2%A0organisations%C2%A0(CSOs)%20have%20been%20opposed%20to%20bringing%20the%C2%A0Kuki-dominated%20areas%20under%20the%20Sixth%20Schedule%20and%C2%A0thereby%C2%A0granting%C2%A0them%20a%20%E2%80%9Cseparate%20administration%E2%80%9D%20under%20an%20autonomous%C2%A0territorial%20council.%20They%20feared%20that%C2%A0granting%20a%20separate%20financial%20channel%20to%20them%20directly%20with%20Delhi%C2%A0would%C2%A0amount%20to%C2%A0affecting%C2%A0the%20%E2%80%9Cterritorial%20integrity%E2%80%9D%20of%20the%20Manipur%20state.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20the%20event%20of%20the%20Union%20government%20being%20able%20to%20formalise%20this%20deal%20with%20the%20Kukis%20on%20May%208%2C%20it%20would%20have%20had%20every%20likelihood%20of%20creating%20widespread%20disappointment%20within%20the%20Meitei%20groups%20with%20the%20possibility%20of%20sparking%20protests.%20Sources%20say%20that%20Singh%20being%20on%20the%20chief%20minister%E2%80%99s%20chair%20and%20hailing%20from%20the%20Meitei%20community%2C%20feared%20being%20left%20vulnerable%20directly%20to%20backlash%20from%20his%20%E2%80%98own%E2%80%99%20and%20the%20move%20directly%20affecting%20his%20political%20career.%20Singh%20has%20anyway%20been%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.newindianexpress.com%2Fnation%2Fnortheast%2F2023%2Fapr%2F17%2Fdissidence-brews-against-cm-n-biren-singh-in-manipur-disgruntled-mlas-camping-in-delhi-2566808.html%5C%22%3Efacing%C2%A0protracted%C2%A0rebellion%20from%20within%20his%20party%2C%3C%2Fa%3E%20led%20by%20other%20Meitei%20leaders%C2%A0of%20the%20BJP.%20Batches%20of%20party%20MLAs%20have%20been%20visiting%20New%20Delhi%20till%20as%20late%20as%20this%20April%2C%20demanding%20a%20change%20in%20leadership.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3EThe%20Wire%3C%2Fem%3E%C2%A0reached%20out%20to%20state%20BJP%20leaders%20for%20comments%3B%20but%20all%20of%20them%20refused%20to%20speak%2C%20citing%20no%20knowledge%20of%20the%20proposed%20peace%20accord%20with%20the%C2%A0Kuki%C2%A0SoO%20groups%C2%A0on%20May%208.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EA%20senior%20Congress%20MLA%20and%20a%20former%20colleague%20of%20Singh%20that%20%3Cem%3EThe%20Wire%3C%2Fem%3E%20reached%20out%20said%20he%20was%20unaware%20of%20the%20likely%20proposal.%20He%2C%20however%2C%20said%2C%20%E2%80%9CWhile%20the%20Bharatiya%20Janata%20Party%20(BJP)%20led%20Union%20government%20must%20have%20been%20looking%20at%20securing%20the%20Manipur%20Outer%20parliamentary%20seat%20for%20the%202024%20general%20elections%20by%20granting%20the%20Sixth%20Schedule%20to%20t