%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.wsj.com%2Farticles%2Famazon-deliver-prime-speed-packaging-a616a135%3Fmod%3Dhp_lead_pos3%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EWall%20Street%20Journal%20reported%3C%2Fa%3E.%20Various%20iterations%20of%20these%20packaging%20changes%20have%20been%20around%20at%20Amazon%20since%202015%2C%20the%20company%20told%20Insider.%20This%20current%20change%2C%20to%20eliminate%20or%20cut%20down%20on%20extra%20packaging%20and%20work%20with%20brands%20on%20new%20packaging%20that%20does%20not%20need%20an%20additional%20box%2C%20is%20part%20of%20the%20company's%20efforts%20to%20reduce%20costs%2C%20and%20address%20customer%20feedback%20and%20its%20climate%20impact.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThis%20year%2C%20the%20company%20has%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Famazon-double-same-day-delivery-sites-increase-delivery-speed-2023-7%5C%22%3Edelivered%20around%201.8%20billion%20packages%3C%2Fa%3E%C2%A0%20%E2%80%94%20which%20can%20add%20up%20to%20a%20lot%20of%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Famazons-plastic-air-packets-boxes-circle-the-planet-2022-12%5C%22%3Ediscarded%20Amazon%20packaging%3C%2Fa%3E.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBut%20the%20new%20packaging%2C%20or%20lack%20thereof%2C%20could%20cause%20some%20concerns.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20Journal%20notes%20that%20items%20like%20toilet%20paper%2C%20baby%20wipes%2C%20trash%20bags%2C%20and%20Brita%20water%20filters%20could%20start%20showing%20up%20in%20their%20original%20packaging%20for%20all%20your%20neighbors%20to%20see.%20Besides%20the%20potential%20embarrassment%20of%20publicizing%20your%20purchases%2C%20there's%20a%20more%20practical%20concern%20of%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fguides%2Ftech%2Fwhat-to-do-if-your-package-gets-stolen%5C%22%3Epackage%20theft%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ETo%20address%20those%20concerns%2C%20Amazon%20shoppers%20do%20still%20have%20the%20option%20to%20select%20extra%20packaging%20at%20no%20additional%20cha