e%20announcement%20that%20with%20this%20%26quot%3Bonce-in-a-generation%20investment%2C%26quot%3B%20the%20DOE%20%26quot%3Bis%20laying%20the%20foundation%20for%20a%20direct%20air%20capture%20industry%20crucial%20to%20tackling%20climate%20change%20%E2%80%94%20transforming%20local%20economies%20and%20delivering%20healthier%20communities%20along%20the%20way.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%3EHow%20direct%20air%20capture%20differs%20from%20carbon%20capture%20technology%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EUnlike%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fcarbon-capture-storage-expensive-climate-change-2021-9%5C%22%3Ecarbon%20capture%20technology%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20which%20captures%20carbon%20as%20its%20being%20produced%20by%20a%20facility%20before%20it%20reaches%20the%20atmosphere%2C%20direct%20air%20capture%20acts%20like%20a%20giant%20air%20purifier%2C%20separating%20carbon%20that%20is%20already%20in%20the%20air%20and%20pumping%20it%20underground%20or%20into%20rocks%20for%20permanent%20storage.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20Texas%20site%20believes%20it%20could%20store%20up%20to%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fmarkets.businessinsider.com%2Fnews%2Fstocks%2F1pointfive-selected-for-u-s-department-of-energy-grant-to-develop-south-texas-direct-air-capture-hub-1032546036%5C%22%3E3%20billion%20metric%20tons%20of%20CO%3Csub%3E2%3C%2Fsub%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%20in%20saline%20formations%20under%20the%20hub.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThese%20sites%20are%20part%20of%20a%20four-pronged%20plan%20pushed%20by%20the%20Biden-Harris%20administration%20to%20limit%20warming%20to%20just%20no%20more%20than%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fclimate-change-alter-human-life-un-ipcc-report-2022-2%5C%22%3E1.5%20degrees%20Celsius%2C%3C%2Fa%3E%20by%20reducing%20emissions%20by%2050%25%20to%2052%25%20by%202030.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ETo%20do%20so%2C%20the%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.whitehouse.gov%2Fbriefing-room%2Fspeeches-remarks%2F2023%2F04%2F20%2Fremarks-by-president-biden-at-the-2023-major-econ