809_1.html%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.business-standard.com%2Famp%2Fcompanies%2Fnews%2Findustry-s-ev-sales-could-rise-by-10-times-in-5-years-says-tata-motors-123081100809_1.html%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%2228%20Students%20Hospitalised%20After%20Suspected%20Gas%20Leak%20Near%20Delhi%20School%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3ETwenty-eight%20students%20of%20a%20municipal%20school%20in%20west%20Delhi's%20Naraina%20area%20were%20hospitalised%20on%20Friday%20with%20two%20of%20them%20requiring%20oxygen%20support%20after%20allegedly%20inhaling%20noxious%20fumes%20following%20a%20suspected%20%26quot%3Bgas%20leak%26quot%3B%20incident%20nearby%2C%20officials%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EDelhi%20Mayor%20Shelly%20Oberoi%20said%20the%20students%2C%20including%20two%20girls%20who%20were%20put%20on%20oxygen%20support%20in%20Ram%20Manohar%20Lohia%20(RML)%20Hospital%2C%20are%20doing%20fine.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Aam%20Aadmi%20Party's%20MCD%20in-charge%20Durgesh%20Pathak%2C%20who%20met%20the%20ailing%20students%20at%20the%20hospital%2C%20said%20it%20is%20being%20claimed%20that%20the%20gas%20leaked%20from%20a%20train%20that%20was%20passing%20the%20railway%20tracks%20nearby.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Municipal%20Corporation%20of%20Delhi%20(MCD)%2C%20in%20a%20statement%2C%20said%2C%20%26quot%3BThe%20gas%20leak%20occurred%20at%20the%20nearby%20railway%20tracks.%26quot%3B%20However%2C%20the%20Railways%2C%20in%20a%20statement%2C%20said%20they%20have%20not%20received%20any%20report%20of%20gas%20leak%20from%20any%20station%20and%20asserted%20that%20their%20wagons%20never%20transport%20any%20toxic%20gas%20that%20may%20pose%20a%20health%20hazard.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20MCD%2C%20in%20a%20statement%2C%20said%20that%2019%20students%20were%20admitted%20to%20RML%20Hospital%20and%20nine%20at%20Acharya%20Bhikshuk%20Hospital.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAll%20the%20nine%20students%20admitted%20at%20Acharya%20Bhikshuk%20Hospital%20have%20been%20discharged.%20Of%20the%2019%20students%20admitted%20in%20RML%2C%2015%20came%20by%2011.28%20am.%20Four%20more%20came%20after%203%20pm%2C%20it%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20civic%20body%20said%20all%20the%20students%20who%20were%20admitted%20to%20the%20hospital%20by%2011.28%20am%20are%20being%20discharged%20except%20one%20who%20has%20some%20pre-existing%20chronic%20gastric%20problem.%20%26quot%3BHence%2C%2014%20students%20are%20being%20discharged%20and%20five%20are%20kept%20for%20observation.%20A%20teacher%20will%20stay%20in%20the%20hospital%20overnight%20to%20take%20care%20of%20the%20students.%26quot%3B%20Some%20parents%20of%20the%20affected%20children%20alleged%20the%20school%20authorities%20did%20not%20inform%20them%20about%20the%20incident.%20Children%2C%20who%20became%20ill%2C%20said%20they%20experienced%20stomach%20aches%20and%20breathing%20difficulty%20due%20to%20the%20foul%20smell.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EPolice%20said%20they%20received%20a%20call%20about%20some%20students%20falling%20sick%20and%20vomiting%20at%20Nigam%20Pratibha%20Vidyalaya%20in%20Inderpuri.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BAccording%20to%20initial%20assessment%2C%20a%20foul%20smell%20filled%20some%20classrooms%2C%20which%20made%20the%20children%20feel%20sick.%20Apparently%2C%20the%20children%20had%20just%20eaten.%20The%20smell%20has%20subsided%2C%20but%20as%20a%20precaution%2C%20all%20classrooms%20have%20been%20vacated%2C%26quot%3B%20Deputy%20Commissioner%20of%20Police%20(West)%20Vichitra%20Veer%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20senior%20officer%20said%20further%20examination%20of%20the%20premises%20is%20being%20done%20to%20ascertain%20the%20source%20of%20the%20smell.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThere%20is%20a%20railway%20track%20nearby.%20However%2C%20it%20is%20yet%20to%20be%20ascertained%20where%20the%20smell%20was%20emanating%20from%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EFollowing%20the%20incident%2C%20officials%20from%20the%20civic%20health%20department%20rushed%20to%20the%20two%20hospitals%20and%20the%20school.%20The%20education%20department%20of%20the%20MCD%20is%20also%20on%20the%20job%2C%20the%20official%20added.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWe%20will%20probe%20at%20our%20level%20too%20to%20find%20out%20what%20caused%20this%20incident%2C%26quot%3B%20the%20senior%20official%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EA%20student's%20father%20said%2C%20%26quot%3BWe%20went%20to%20the%20school%20where%20some%20people%20said%20children%20have%20been%20taken%20to%20RML%20hospital.%20That%20is%20how%20we%20came%20here.%26quot%3B%20Another%20parent%20said%2C%20%26quot%3BAfter%20we%20learnt%20about%20the%20incident%2C%20we%20checked%20the%20nearby%20hospitals.%20Then%20a%20person%20told%20us%20that%20our%20children%20are%20in%20RML%20Hospital.%20We%20have%20been%20told%20that%20they%20ate%20something%20following%20which%20they%20fell%20ill.%26quot%3B%20AAP%20leader%20Durgesh%20Pathak%20said%20that%20preliminary%20examination%20by%20doctors%20has%20ruled%20out%20the%20possibility%20of%20food%20poisoning.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BInvestigation%20is%20underway%20to%20ascertain%20where%20this%20gas%20came%20from%20since%20there%20was%20nothing%20in%20the%20school%20that%20could%20have%20led%20to%20it.%20People%20are%20saying%20that%20a%20train%20was%20passing%20by%20and%20possibly%20this%20gas%20came%20from%20there.%20An%20MCD%20team%20is%20probing%20it%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EA%20railway%20spokesperson%20said%20train%20wagons%20never%20transport%20any%20toxic%20gases%20which%20may%20pose%20any%20health%20hazard.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BMoreover%20no%20such%20report%20of%20gas%20leakage%20has%20been%20reported%20from%20any%20station%20and%20there%20was%20no%20movement%20of%20any%20trains%20having%20gaseous%20contents%20passing%20in%20the%20area%20indicated%20during%20the%20time%20of%20incidence%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOberoi%20met%20the%20ailing%20students%20and%20said%20they%20were%20doing%20fine.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BI%20inform%20with%20a%20great%20feeling%20of%20relief%20that%20the%20two%20girls%20who%20were%20in%20RML%20on%20oxygen%20support%20are%20fine%20now.%20All%20the%20children%20admitted%20to%20both%20hospitals%20are%20fine%20now.%20We%20are%20working%20to%20rehabilitate%20the%20children%20to%20the%20safe%20confines%20of%20their%20homes%20now.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BDelhi%20Crime's%20Forensic%20team%20visited%20the%20school%20today.%20They%20will%20submit%20the%20report%20identifying%20the%20exact%20reason%2C%26quot%3B%20she%20said%20in%20a%20post%20on%20social%20media%20site%20X%2C%20formerly%20known%20as%20Twitter.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20MCD%2C%20in%20a%20statement%2C%20said%20officials%20have%20been%20directed%20to%20probe%20the%20incident%20and%20find%20the%20cause%20as%20well%20as%20the%20source%20of%20the%20gas%20leak.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EDelhi%20BJP%20president%20Virendra%20Sachdeva%20met%20the%20students%20at%20RML%20hospital.%20He%20said%20neither%20the%20students%20nor%20the%20teachers%20were%20able%20to%20say%20what%20caused%20the%20incident%20and%20the%20civic%20body%20should%20probe%20the%20matter.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThe%20students%20said%20they%20were%20sitting%20in%20their%20classroom%20when%20they%20got%20a%20very%20strong%20smell%20which%20caused%20vomiting%20and%20unconsciousness%2C%26quot%3B%20the%20BJP%20leader%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20a%20statement%2C%20Sachdeva%20accused%20the%20AAP%20of%20%26quot%3Bmisleading%26quot%3B%20the%20families%20of%20students%20by%20saying%20they%20have%20been%20affected%20by%20a%20gas%20leak.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%202017%2C%20a%20chemical%20leak%20from%20the%20Tughlakabad%20container%20depot%20had%20affected%20over%20450%20girl%20students%2C%20a%20few%20teachers%20and%20some%20residents.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Ci%3E(Except%20for%20the%20headline%2C%20this%20story%20has%20not%20been%20edited%20by%20NDTV%20staff%20and%20is%20published%20from%20a%20syndicated%20feed.)%3C%2Fi%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1691773440000%2C