her%20was%20by%20Tarun%20Gogoi%2C%20who%20gave%20this%20rank%20opportunist%20positions%20of%20power%20and%20authority.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%2054-year-old%2C%20once%20considered%20the%20blue-eyed%20boy%20of%20former%20Assam%20Chief%20Ministers%20Hiteswar%20Saikia%20and%20Tarun%20Gogoi%2C%20quit%20the%20Congress%20in%202015%20after%20he%20fell%20out%20with%20Mr%20Gogoi.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIt's%20not%20like%20the%20Congress%20gave%20me%20a%20chance%20in%20politics.%20I%20proved%20it%20to%20even%20Gogoi%20sir%20that%20I%20was%20in%20Assam%20because%20I%20belong%20here%20and%20not%20due%20to%20him.%20Hiteswar%20Saikia%20didn't%20bring%20me%20into%20Congress.%20I%20got%20the%20entire%20Assam%20student%20community%20to%20join%20the%20party%20at%20his%20request.%20Because%20of%20that%2C%20I%20became%20a%20target%20for%20ULFA%2C%26quot%3B%20said%20Mr%20Sarma%20in%20response%20to%20Mr%20Ramesh's%20charge.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMr%20Sarma%2C%20an%20ardent%20critic%20of%20the%20Gandhis%2C%20added%3A%20%26quot%3BI%20don't%20believe%20Gandhis%20gave%20us%20anything.%20It's%20our%20sweat%20and%20blood%20that%20made%20the%20Gandhis.%20People%20say%20Rahul%20(Gandhi)%20or%20Rajiv%20(Gandhi)%20propped%20someone%20up.%20But%20it%20is%20the%20street%20soldier%20who%20gives%20his%20blood.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHe%20also%20called%20Jairam%20Ramesh%20the%20courtier%20of%20Gandhis%2C%20who%20%26quot%3Bruled%20in%20Delhi%26quot%3B%3A%20%26quot%3BThe%20Gandhis%20ruled%20in%20Delhi%20and%20people%20like%20Jairam%20Ramesh%20are%20courtiers%20and%20courtiers%20don't%20know%20the%20reality%20of%20politics.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHimanta%20Biswa%20Sarma%2C%20who%20had%20deftly%20managed%20the%202006%20and%202011%20election%20campaigns%20for%20the%20party%20in%20Assam%2C%20joined%20the%20BJP%20in%20August%202015%20following%20differences%20with%20the%20then%20Congress%20leadership.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1691771820000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2