.%20I%20want%20Muslims%20to%20realise%20their%20relationship%20with%20the%20Congress%20is%20all%20about%20votes%2C%26quot%3B%20Mr%20Sarma%20told%20NDTV.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BDon't%20give%20me%20votes.%20Let%20me%20develop%20your%20areas%20in%20the%20next%2010%20years.%20I%20want%20to%20ensure%20child%20marriage%20practice%20ends%2C%20stop%20going%20to%20madrasas.%20Go%20to%20colleges%20instead.%20I%20am%20going%20to%20inaugurate%20seven%20colleges%20for%20Muslim%20daughters%2C%20especially%20girls%2C%26quot%3B%20Mr%20Sarma%20told%20NDTV.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMr%20Sarma%2C%20who%20succeeded%20Sarbananda%20Sonowal%20as%20the%2015th%20Chief%20Minister%20of%20Assam%20in%202021%20after%20the%20BJP's%20second%20consecutive%20win%20in%20the%20northeast%20state%2C%20explained%20why%20it%20is%20important%20for%20Muslims%20to%20understand%20that%20their%20relationship%20with%20the%20BJP%20is%20beyond%20votes.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThe%20Congress%20did%20not%20build%20infrastructure%20or%20schools%20in%20Muslim%20areas.%20But%20I%20want%20to%20develop%20them.%20I%20will%20do%20this%20for%2010-15%20years%2C%20then%20I%20will%20ask%20for%20votes%20from%20Muslims.%20If%20I%20ask%20for%20votes%20from%20them%20now%2C%20it%20will%20become%20a%20give%20and%20take%20relationship.%20I%20don't%20want%20it%20to%20be%20a%20transactional%20relationship%2C%26quot%3B%20the%20Chief%20Minister%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMr%20Sarma%20said%20he%20decided%20not%20to%20campaign%20in%20Muslim%20areas%20in%20the%20last%20state%20election%20too.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIn%202016%20and%202020%2C%20during%20campaigning%2C%20I%20did%20not%20go%20to%20Muslim%20areas.%20I%20had%20said%20I%20would%20go%20only%20after%20winning%20the%20election.%20Even%20this%20time%20I%20am%20telling%20them%2C%20vote%20for%20whoever%20you%20want.%20BJP%20will%20not%20campaign%20in%20their%20area%2C%26quot%3B%20Mr%20Sarma%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20BJP%20won%20a%20second%20straight%20term%20in%20the%20assembly%20election%20in%202021%2C%20taking%2060%20seats%20in%20the%20126-member%20Assam%20assembly%2C%20while%20its%20alliance%20partners%20AGP%20got%20nine%20seats%20and%20UPPL%20six%20seats.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMr%20Sarma%2C%20who%20switched%20to%20the%20BJP%20from%20the%20Congress%20in%202015%2C%20is%20credited%20as%20the%20architect%20who%20brought%20the%20northeast%20states%20within%20the%20party's%20grasp.%20He%20also%20handled%20the%20health%20portfolio%20in%20the%20Sarbananda%20Sonowal%20government.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20BJP's%20spectacular%20victory%20in%20the%20Assam%20election%20in%202016%2C%20sweeping%20aside%20the%20Congress's%20Tarun%20Gogoi%20government%20which%20ruled%20the%20state%20for%20three%20successive%20terms%2C%20has%20been%20largely%20credited%20to%20Mr%20Sarma's%20strategies.%20The%20next%20year%2C%20the%20BJP%20formed%20government%20in%20Manipur%20despite%20winning%20fewer%20seats%20than%20the%20Congress.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1691767080000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2023-08%2F5dgvk6m_himanta-biswa-sarma-sanjay-pugalia-650_650x400_11_August_23.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fright-now-i-wont-seek-muslim-votes-himanta-biswa-sarma-exclusive-4290777%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Assam%20Chief%20Minister%20Himanta%20Biswa%20Sarma%20in%20an%20exclusive%20interview%20with%20NDTV%20said%20he%20does%20not%20indulge%20in%20%26quot%3Bvote%20bank%20politics%26quot%3B%20and%20so%2C%20unlike%20the%20Congress%2C%20will%20not%20link%20politics%20with%20issues%20linked%20to%20the%20Muslim%20community.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fright-now-i-wont-seek-muslim-votes-himanta-biswa-sarma-exclusive-4290777%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww-ndtv-com.cdn.ampproject.org%2Fc%2Fs%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fright-now-i-wont-seek-muslim-votes-himanta-biswa-sarma-exclusive-4290777%2Famp%2F