nti-corruption%20ministerial%20meeting%20in%20Kolkata.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20Delhi%2C%20he%20met%20External%20Affairs%20Minister%20S%20Jaishankar%20and%20National%20Security%20Advisor%20Ajit%20Doval.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BDuring%20a%20meeting%20with%20India's%20External%20Affairs%20Minister%2C%20S%20Jaishankar%2C%20in%20New%20Delhi%20on%20Thursday%2C%20Minister%20Tugendhat%20announced%20new%20funding%20to%20enhance%20the%20UK's%20capability%20to%20tackle%20Pro-Khalistan%20Extremism%2C%26quot%3B%20the%20high%20commission%20said%20on%20Friday.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIt%20said%20the%2095%2C000%20pound%20investment%20will%20enhance%20the%20government's%20understanding%20of%20the%20threat%20posed%20by%20%26quot%3Bpro-Khalistan%20extremism%26quot%3B%2C%20complementing%20the%20joint%20work%20already%20underway%20between%20the%20UK%20and%20India%20through%20the%20joint-extremism%20task%20force.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThe%20living%20bridge%20between%20India%20and%20the%20UK%20reflects%20our%20deep%20and%20enduring%20friendship.%20As%20the%20world's%20oldest%20and%20largest%20democracies%2C%20we%20have%20many%20shared%20opportunities%20to%20make%20the%20world%20a%20safer%20and%20more%20prosperous%20place%2C%26quot%3B%20Tugendhat%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BA%20deeper%20partnership%20between%20our%20two%20nations%20means%20we%20can%20more%20effectively%20tackle%20the%20security%20threats%20we%20both%20face.%20I'm%20committed%20to%20working%20together%20to%20enhance%20our%20understanding%20of%20and%20capabilities%20against%20extremism%20--whatever%20form%20it%20takes%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAsked%20about%20the%20British%20minister's%20announcement%20on%20the%20new%20funding%2C%20External%20Affairs%20Ministry%20Spokesperson%20Arindam%20Bagchi%20said%20at%20his%20weekly%20media%20briefing%20that%20it%20is%20the%20UK's%20internal%20matter%20and%20it%20would%20not%20be%20appropriate%20for%20him%20to%20comment%20on%20it.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BCertainly%2C%20we%20have%20been%20emphasising%20the%20need%20for%20the%20UK%20side%20to%20take%20action%20against%20extremists%20and%20radicals%2C%20particularly%20those%20who%20are%20inciting%20violence%20and%20posing%20security%20threats%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMr%20Bagchi%20said%20issues%20relating%20security%20of%20the%20Indian%20mission%20in%20London%20has%20been%20part%20of%20%26quot%3Bongoing%20conversation%26quot%3B%20between%20the%20two%20sides.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BOf%20course%2C%20this%20is%20an%20ongoing%20conversation%20that%20we%20have%20with%20the%20UK%20side%20on%20steps%20that%20we%20feel%20the%20UK%20side%20and%20all%20host%20governments%20need%20to%20take%20to%20protect%20our%20diplomatic%20premises%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMr%20Bagchi%20also%20indicated%20that%20India%20would%20like%20to%20have%20additional%20security%20measures%20in%20view%20of%20India's%20Independence%20Day%20celebrations%20on%20August%2015.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAfter%20his%20talks%20with%20Tugendhat%20on%20Thursday%2C%20S%20Jaishankar%20said%20on%20'X'%20that%20they%20discussed%20how%20India%20and%20the%20United%20Kingdom%20could%20make%20their%20partnership%20more%20contemporary%20and%20productive.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20the%20British%20readout%2C%20Tugendhat%20is%20quoted%20as%20saying%20that%20he%20is%20delighted%20to%20be%20attending%20the%20G20%20meeting.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BCorruption%20also%20harms%20our%20prosperity%2C%20damages%20our%20society%20and%20threatens%20our%20national%20security.%20I%20am%20delighted%20to%20be%20attending%20the%20G20%20anti-corruption%20ministerial%20meeting%2C%20presided%20over%20by%20India%2C%20to%20continue%20strengthening%20global%20resilience%20and%20cracking%20down%20on%20its%20corrosive%20influence%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBefore%20travelling%20to%20Kolkata%20for%20the%20G20%20meeting%2C%20which%20will%20take%20place%20on%20Saturday%2C%20Tugendhat%20was%20scheduled%20to%20visit%20the%20headquarters%20of%20Central%20Bureau%20of%20Investigation%20(CBI)%20to%20discuss%20joint%20challenges%20posed%20by%20child%20sexual%20exploitation%20and%20abuse%2C%20and%20fraud.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBritish%20High%20Commissioner%20to%20India%20Alex%20Ellis%20said%3A%20%26quot%3BThe%20unique%20connection%20between%20our%20people%20brings%20both%20huge%20opportunities%20and%20security%20challenges.%26quot%3B%20%26quot%3BThrough%20mechanisms%20like%20the%20Joint%20Extremism%20Task%20Force%20we%20are%20acting%20jointly%20on%20countering%20threats%2C%20including%20pro-Khalistan%20extremism%2C%20as%20well%20as%20on%20migration%2C%20to%20keep%20our%20people%20safe%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EEllis%20said%20the%20migration%20and%20mobility%20relationship%20between%20the%20two%20countries%20is%20a%20%26quot%3Bpillar%20of%20our%20comprehensive%20strategic%20partnership%26quot%3B%20that%20also%20includes%20ensuring%20a%20free%20and%20open%20Indo%20Pacific%2C%20and%20tackling%20the%20biggest%20challenges%20facing%20the%20world%20around%20climate%20and%20health.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThis%20is%20a%20partnership%20for%20now%2C%20including%20India's%20G20%20Presidency%2C%20and%20for%20the%20future%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20added.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBritish%20officials%20maintained%20that%20the%20security%20of%20the%20Indian%20High%20Commission%20in%20London%20and%20its%20staff%2C%20are%20of%20utmost%20importance%20to%20the%20UK%20government.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Ci%3E(Except%20for%20the%20headline%2C%20this%20story%20has%20not%20been%20edited%20by%20NDTV%20staff%20and%20is%20published%20from%20a%20syndicated%20feed.)%3C%2Fi%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1691765040000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2023-08%2Fddf4i2dc_uk-minister-1200_625x300_11_August_23.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fuk-announces-new-funding-to-deal-with-pro-khalistani-extremism-4290