%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F08%2Fmission-muskaan-1-1691757574.jpg%201200w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F08%2Fmission-muskaan-1-1691757574-300x157.jpg%20300w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F08%2Fmission-muskaan-1-1691757574-500x262.jpg%20500w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F08%2Fmission-muskaan-1-1691757574-768x402.jpg%20768w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F08%2Fmission-muskaan-1-1691757574-150x79.jpg%20150w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-327081%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22628%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%20class%3D%5C%22wp-element-caption%5C%22%3EThese%20children%20get%20involved%20in%20different%20sports%20activities%20and%20are%20engaged%20in%20making%20crafts%20and%20paintings.%20%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EFor%20this%20purpose%2C%20he%20utilises%20funds%20from%20the%20district%20administration.%20Himanshu%20says%20the%20activities%20at%20the%20child%20care%20homes%20are%20supervised%20regularly.%20%E2%80%9CI%20personally%20visit%20at%20least%20one%20home%20every%20week.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHighlighting%20challenges%20to%20run%20the%20campaign%2C%20he%20says%2C%20%E2%80%9CUsually%20it%20takes%205-15%20days%20or%20more%20to%20reunite%20children%20with%20their%20families.%20But%20not%20all%20kids%20are%20the%20same.%20Some%20are%20intellectually%20disabled%20and%20it%20takes%20time%20to%20identify%20their%20homes%20as%20they%20are%20not%20able%20to%20communicate%20effectively.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EFor%20instance%2C%20Saurabh%20Maurya%2C%20who%20accompanies%20children%20to%20their%20homes%2C%20tells%20%3Cstrong%3EThe%20Better%20India%2C%20%3C%2Fstrong%3E%E2%80%9CIn%20the%20case%20of%20Shoaib%2C%20we%20had%20to%20use%20his%20biometrics%20to%20get%20his%20Aadhaar%20card%2C%20and%20address%20details%2C%20because%20he%20was%20unable%20to%20communicate%20about%20his%20home%20an