0book%2C%20%3Cem%3EThe%20Anglo-Kuki%20War%201917-1919%3A%20A%20Frontier%20Uprising%20Against%20Imperialism%20During%20the%20First%20World%20War%3C%2Fem%3E%2C%20is%20written%20by%20retired%20Colonel%20Dr%20Vijay%20Chenji.%20It%20is%20edited%20by%20Jawaharlal%20Nehru%20University%20assistant%20professors%20Jangkhomang%20Guite%20and%20Thongkholal%20Haokip%2C%20who%20teach%20at%20the%20university%E2%80%99s%20Centre%20for%20Historical%20Studies%20and%20the%20Centre%20for%20the%20Study%20of%20Law%20and%20Governance.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Famp.scroll.in%2Flatest%2F1054175%2Fmanipur-police-book-author-two-academicians-for-allegedly-distorting-states-history%5C%22%3E%3Cem%3EScroll.in%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%20has%20reported%20that%20two%20FIRs%20were%20filed.%20The%20one%20against%20Chenji%20was%20filed%20on%20August%209%2C%20while%20the%20case%20against%20Guite%20and%20Haokip%20was%20registered%20on%20August%207.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20book%20was%20published%20in%202018.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20complaint%2C%20filed%20by%20individuals%20from%20the%20Ukhrul%2C%20Imphal%20East%20and%20Imphal%20West%20villages%20alleges%20that%20the%20accused%20have%20disseminated%20falsehood%20and%20created%20an%20environment%20against%20public%20peace%20by%20representing%20the%20armed%20Kuki%20rebellion%20of%201917-1919%20as%20an%20Anglo-Kuki%20war.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3EScroll.in%3C%2Fem%3E%E2%80%98s%20report%20says%20that%20the%20civil%20society%20organisation%20Federation%20of%20Haomee%20had%20the%20complaints%20filed.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20complainants%20have%20claimed%20that%20in%20the%20history%20of%20Manipur%20and%20the%20United%20Kingdom%2C%20there%20has%20never%20been%20an%20Anglo-Kuki%20war%2C%20and%20that%20the%20Kuki%20rebellion%20involved%20the%20massacre%20of%20Nagas%20and%20Koms%20in%20the%20hill%20areas%20and%20Meiteis%20and%20Muslims%20in%20the%20Valley.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20three%20have%20been%20charged%20against%20section%20120%20(concealing%20design%20to%20commit%20offence%20punishable%20with%20imprisonment)%2C%20121%20(waging%2C%20or%20attempting%20to%20wage%20war%2C%20or%20abetting%20waging%20of%20war%2C%20against%20the%20government%20of%20India)%2C%20123%20(concealing%20with%20intent%20to%20facilitate%20design%20to%20wage%20war)%2C%20153-A%20(promoting%20enmity%20between%20different%20groups%20on%20grounds%20of%20religion%2C%20race%2C%20place%20of%20birth%2C%20residence%2C%20language%2C%20etc.%2C%20and%20doing%20acts%20prejudicial%20to%20maintenance%20of%20harmony)%2C%20200%20(whoever%20corruptly%20uses%20or%20attempts%20to%20use%20as%20true%20any%20such%20declaration%2C%20knowing%20the%20same%20to%20be%20false%20in%20any%20material%20point%2C%20shall%20be%20punished%20in%20the%20same)%20and%20120-B%20(whoever%20is%20a%20party%20to%20a%20criminal%20conspiracy%20other%20than%20a%20criminal%20conspiracy%20to%20commit%20an%20offence%20punishable%20as%20aforesaid).%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20state%20of%20Manipur%20has%20seen%20100%20days%20of%20brutal%20ethnic%20violence%20between%20Meitei%20and%20Kuki%20communities.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1691758636000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F05%2F29204217%2FWhatsApp-Image-2023-05-29-at-7.07.45-PM.jpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fgovernment%2Fmanipur-police-anglo-kuki-war-book-fir%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22The%20book%2C%20'The%20Anglo-Kuki%20War%201917-1919%3A%20A%20Frontier%20Uprising%20Against%20Imperialism%20During%20the%20First%20World%20War%2C'%20was%20written%20by%20retired%20Colonel%20Dr%20Vijay%20Chenji%20and%20edited%20by%20two%20JNU%20assistant%20professors.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A23%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fgovernment%2Fmanipur-police-anglo-kuki-war-book-fir%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22K2%3A%20Climbers%20deny%20walking%20by%20dying%20guide%20in%20bid%20t