om%20has%20patches%20of%20roof%20that%20have%20collapsed%20over%20the%20years.%20They%20make%20temporary%20repairs%2C%20but%20in%20the%20rainy%20season%2C%20these%20issues%20worsen.%20There%20is%20always%20a%20heavy%20influx%20of%20patients%20and%20if%20we%20need%20to%20provide%20better%20services%2C%20then%20we%20need%20better%20maintenance%20of%20the%20building%20as%20well%2C%E2%80%9D%20said%20Dr%20Kadali%20Vishni%2C%20who%20passed%20out%20from%20OMC%20in%202014%20to%20The%20News%20Minute.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThis%20led%20to%20a%20renewed%20push%20by%20politicians%20to%20demolish%20the%20structure%20and%20build%20a%20new%20hospital.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWhat%20everyone%20unanimously%20agrees%20upon%2C%20is%20the%20fact%20that%20the%20building%20is%20in%20urgent%20need%20of%20repair%20and%20restoration.%20While%20Telangana%20Chief%20Minister%20K%20Chandrashekar%20Rao%20wants%20the%20entire%20structure%20to%20be%20demolished%2C%20conservation%20architects%20want%20it%20to%20be%20restored.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cfigure%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-embed%20wp-block-embed-twitter%5C%22%3E%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-embed__wrapper%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cblockquote%20data-width%3D%5C%22500%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22twitter-tweet%5C%22%20data-dnt%3D%5C%22true%5C%22%3E%3Cp%20lang%3D%5C%22en%5C%22%20dir%3D%5C%22ltr%5C%22%3EFirst%20light%20hitting%20Osmania%20general%20hospital%2C%20Hyderabad.%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2Fhashtag%2FHyderabad%3Fsrc%3Dhash%26ref_src%3Dtwsrc%255Etfw%5C%22%3E%23Hyderabad%3C%2Fa%3E%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2Fhashtag%2FTelangana%3Fsrc%3Dhash%26ref_src%3Dtwsrc%255Etfw%5C%22%3E%23Telangana%3C%2Fa%3E%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ft.co%2FiEiCH5Yt98%5C%22%3Epic.twitter.com%2FiEiCH5Yt98%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%E2%80%94%20Mohammed%20Awaise%20(%40awaisevisuals)%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2Fawaisevisuals%2Fstatus%2F1689132269171302401%3Fref_src%3Dtwsrc%255Etfw%5C%22%3EAugust%209%2C%202023%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fblockquote%3E%5Cn%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EConservation%20architects%20and%20historians%2C%20however%2C%20have%20been%20arguing%20for%20saving%20the%20heritage%20building%20%E2%80%94%20which%20is%20built%20on%201%20acre%20%E2%80%94%20and%20building%20a%20new%20hospital%20around%20it.%20The%20structure%20is%20graded%20a%20II-B%20Heritage%20Building%20in%20Hyderabad%20Metropolitan%20Development%20Association%20(HMDA)%20Listing%20and%20is%20protected%20under%20the%20Heritage%20Regulations%20of%20HMDA.%20A%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%20nofollow%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.change.org%2Fp%2Fchief-minister-of-telangana-save-osmania-general-hospital-protect-heritage-and-health-4fbf6b85-6026-49bf-be1f-27db734c767e%3Frecruiter%3D970031523%26utm_source%3Dshare_petition%26utm_medium%3Dtwitter%26utm_campaign%3Dpsf_combo_share_initial%26utm_term%3Dpsf_combo_share_initial%26recruited_by_id%3D8fac0dc0-8cce-11e9-a283-b56392a0b6fb%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%3Cem%3Echange.org%20%3C%2Fem%3Epetition%3C%2Fa%3E%20was%20started%20in%20July%202020%20to%20%E2%80%98Save%20Osmania%20General%20Hospital-Protect%20Heritage%20and%20Health%E2%80%99%2C%20which%20received%20more%20than%2014%2C000%20signatures.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CThis%20is%20not%20just%20a%20building%20but%20it%20is%20the%20skyline%20of%20the%20city.%20The%20entire%20Musi%20and%20the%20banks%20of%20it%20tell%20the%20story%20of%20the%20city%20and%20how%20it%20took%20shape%2C%E2%80%9D%20said%20conservation%20architect%20GSV%20Suryanarayana%20Murthy%20to%20The%20Print.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20August%202015%20and%202019%2C%20INTACH%20(Indian%20National%20Trust%20for%20Art%20and%20Cultural%20Heritage)%20published%20a%20report%20stating%20that%20the%20building%20was%20in%20a%20%E2%80%9Cvery%20good%20and%20structurally%20stable%20condition%20and%20did%20not%20pose%20a%20threat%20to%20its%20occupants%E2%80%9D.%20In%20November%202019%2C%20Telangana%E2%80%99s%20Department%20of%20Archaeology%20and%20Museums%20and%20the%20Aga%20Khan%20Trust%20for%20Culture%20published%20a%20report%20that%20stated%20that%20the%20heritage%20building%20need%20not%20be%20demolished.%20Both%20reports%20state%20that%20the%20building%20should%20be%20restored%20based%20on%20heritage%20conservation%20principles.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CTaking%20everything%20into%20consideration%2C%20we%20observed%20that%20the%20heritage%20building%20is%20safe%20for%20another%20century%2C%20however%20it%20requires%20some%20repairs.%20The%20way%20the%20building%20was%20built%20shows%20how%20well%20it%20was%20planned%20%E2%80%94%20there%20was%20a%20lot%20of%20ventilation%2C%20large%20corridors%2C%20and%20proper%20outlets%20for%20the%20water.%20The%20damage%20caused%20to%20it%20is%20purely%20due%20to%20%E2%80%98unscientific%20intervention%E2%80%99.%20There%20was%20also%20a%20park%20opposite%20to%20the%20hospital%20for%20people%20to%20relax%2C%20which%20has%20been%20destroyed%2C%E2%80%9D%20said%20Anuradha%20Reddy%20of%20INTACH%20to%20%3Cem%3EThe%20Print%3C%2Fem%3E.%C2%A0%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CYou%20have%20to%20have%20a%20basic%20sense%20of%20history%2C%20culture%2C%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thebetterindia.com%2F306528%2Fshrey-gupta-converts-heritage-bungalow-into-luxury-hotel-nainital-gethia-blue-book-hotels%2F%5C%22%3Eheritage%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20and%20an%20idea%20of%20its%20importance.%20These%20are%20markers%20of%20identity%2C%20these%20are%20icons%20of%20the%20past%20%E2%80%94%20if%20you%20don%E2%80%99t%20retain%20that%2C%20Hyderabad%20is%20no%20longer%20a%20400-year-old%20city%2C%E2%80%9D%20said%20Sajjad%20Shahid%2C%20a%20historian%20and%20conservation%20activist%2C%20to%20%3Cem%3ECaravan%3C%2Fem%3E.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch5%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3ESources%3C%2Fh5%3E%5Cn%3Ch5%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3E%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%20nofollow%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thenewsminute.com%2Farticle%2Fdemolition-