t%20Rohan%20Jaitley%20will%20have%20a%20word%20with%20them%20but%20DDCA%20didn't%20even%20stop%20Virender%20Sehwag%20from%20leaving%20the%20state%2C%26quot%3B%20a%20DDCA%20director%20told%20PTI%20on%20conditions%20of%20anonymity.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIt%20remains%20to%20be%20seen%20if%20DDCA%20lures%20Rana%20with%20captaincy.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWhen%20Manchanda%20was%20asked%20if%20Rana%20and%20Shorey%2C%20who%20are%20also%20best%20buddies%20in%20the%20set-up%20will%20have%20their%20grievances%20addressed%2C%20he%20said%3A%20%26quot%3BHow%20can%20we%20talk%20about%20selection%20matters%3F%20It%20is%20the%20prerogative%20of%20selection%20committee.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%3E%3Cstrong%3EHimmat%20Singh%20favourite%20to%20lead%20Delhi%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHimmat%20Singh%2C%20the%20gutsy%20middle-order%20batter%2C%20is%20tipped%20to%20take%20over%20Ranji%20Trophy%20captaincy%20this%20season%20as%20most%20people%20in%20DDCA%20agree%20that%20it%20was%20hasty%20decision%20to%20hand%20over%20captaincy%20to%20Dhull%2C%20who%20had%20till%20then%2C%20had%20played%20only%20one%20first-class%20season.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHowever%2C%20Dhull%20is%20very%20much%20in%20the%20national%20selection%20committee's%20radar%20for%20India%20A%20as%20he%20is%20among%20the%20NCA%20Targeted%20players'%20list%20and%20has%20been%20called%20for%20a%20camp%2C%20the%20reason%20why%20he%20won't%20be%20playing%20the%20Buchi%20Babu%20Trophy%20in%20Chennai.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BYash%20has%20been%20called%20for%20a%20camp%20in%20NCA%20along%20with%20Navdeep%20Saini.%20He%20will%20not%20play%20in%20the%20Buchi%20Babu%20Trophy.%20We%20are%20looking%20at%20Himmat%20as%20a%20potential%20leader.%20He%20is%20someone%20who%20never%20runs%20away%20from%20challenges%2C%26quot%3B%20a%20senior%20DDCA%20official%20privy%20to%20developments%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIt%20is%20also%20learnt%20that%20Abhay%20Sharma%20is%20unlikely%20to%20continue%20as%20Delhi%20team's%20head%20coach.%3C%2