2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20traditional%20media%20and%20their%20gatekeepers%20are%20still%20reeling%20from%20what%20has%20hit%20them.%20They%20have%20been%20seamlessly%20superseded%20by%20an%20ostensibly%20democratic%20and%20deadly-effective%20communication%20web%20which%20enables%20anyone%20with%20a%20smartphone%20to%20have%20their%20message%20conveyed%20across%20the%20world%20instantaneously.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ERegrettably%2C%20this%20marvel%20of%20hi-tech%20that%20is%20full%20of%20endless%20possibilities%20for%20social%20good%2C%20has%20transmuted%20into%20a%20fearsome%20monster%20whose%20first%20targets%20are%20the%20truth%2C%20the%20facts%20and%20sheer%20humaneness.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cins%3EAlso%20Read%3A%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fcommunalism%2Fintricate-design-of-right-wing-propaganda-in-india%5C%22%3EThe%20Intricate%20Design%20of%20Propaganda%20and%20Narrative%20Manipulation%20in%20India%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fins%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20the%20early%20years%2C%20social%20media%20gave%20hope%20of%20transforming%20the%20world%20for%20the%20better.%20A%20truly%20epochal%20information-spreading%20tool%2C%20it%20promised%20a%20global%20society%20rooted%20in%20democracy%2C%20pluralism%20and%20a%20meaningful%20equality.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EConsider%20its%20positive%20forceful%20impact%20in%20a%20deeply%20racist%20country%20like%20America%2C%20where%20even%20as%20late%20as%20the%201990s%2C%20two%20professors%20bestowed%20respectability%20to%20racism%20with%20their%20egregious%20theory%20of%20the%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen.wikipedia.org%2Fwiki%2FThe_Bell_Curve%5C%22%3E%E2%80%9CBell%20Curve%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20which%20sought%20to%20establish%20a%20genetic%20link%20between%20race%20and%20intelligence%2C%20clearly%20insinuating%20that%20whites%20were%20intellectually%20superior%20to%20blacks.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAnd%20yet%20in%20that%20benighted%20land%20a%20decade%20later%2C%20a%20black%20American%20with%20a%20Muslim%20middle%20name%20assumed%20charge%20as%20the%20commander-in-chief.%20In%202008%2C%20fuelled%20by%20a%20brilliantly%20innovative%2C%20multi-pronged%20social%20media%20campaign%2C%20Barack%20Hussein%20Obama%20became%20the%20first%20black%20President%20of%20the%20USA.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHis%20rousing%20rallying%20cry%2C%20%E2%80%9CYes%2C%20we%20can!%E2%80%9D%20ricocheted%20around%20the%20internet%20along%20with%20his%20hope-filled%20message%3A%20%E2%80%9CWe%20will%20begin%20the%20next%20great%20chapter%20in%20the%20American%20story%20with%20three%20words%20that%20will%20ring%20from%20coast%20to%20coast%2C%20from%20sea%20to%20shining%20sea.%E2%80%9D%20Social%20media%20had%20indubitably%20helped%20push%20back%20the%20racist%20bigots%2C%20but%20as%20it%20turned%20out%2C%20only%20fleetingly.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAnd%20who%20can%20forget%20the%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.theguardian.com%2Fworld%2F2011%2Ffeb%2F25%2Ftwitter-facebook-uprisings-arab-libya%5C%22%3Eseminal%20role%20played%20by%20social%20media%3C%2Fa%3E%20in%20the%20revolutionary%20movements%20for%20democracy%20in%20the%20Middle%20East%20and%20North%20Africa%20between%202010%20and%202012%3F%20Social%20media%20helped%20protesters%20to%20mobilise%20support%2C%20shape%20opinions%2C%20organise%20mass%20demonstrations%20and%20inform%20the%20world%20of%20what%20was%20happening%20in%20the%20autocracies%20of%20the%20region.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20a%20dramatic%20reversal%20of%20roles%2C%20state%20propaganda%20was%20overwhelmed%20by%20a%20social%20media%20blitzkrieg%20that%20amplified%20the%20dissenting%20voices%20of%20the%20common%20citizens.%20Social%20media%20had%20struck%20a%20decisive%20blow%20for%20democracy%20by%20helping%20unseat%20an%20unsavoury%20gang%20of%20autocrats.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-caption%5C%22%3E%3Cimg%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2017%2F06%2F1024px-2011_Egyptian_protests_Facebook__jan25_card.jpg%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%22840%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-153149%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22596%5C%22%3E%3Cp%20class%3D%5C%22wp-caption-text%5C%22%3EA%20protester%20holding%20a%20placard%20in%20Cairo%20referring%20to%20Facebook%2C%20acknowledging%20social%20media%E2%80%99s%20role%20during%20the%202011%20Egyptian%20Revolution.%20Photo%3A%20Essam%20Sharaf%2FWikimedia%20Commons.%20CC%20BY-SA%203.0%20Unported.%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBut%20these%20laudable%20exemplars%20of%20the%20potential%20of%20social%20media%20to%20democratise%20global%20discourse%20and%20promote%20the%20common%20good%20proved%20deceptive.%20In%20the%20fractious%20arena%20of%20power%20politics%2C%20social%20media%20has%20become%20the%20prime%20means%20of%20communication%2C%20but%20that%20weighty%20responsibility%20has%20not%20been%20complemented%20by%20responsible%20behaviour.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAnd%20the%20tech%20companies%20%E2%80%93%20the%20putative%20gatekeepers%20%E2%80%93%20have%20been%20cussedly%20reluctant%20to%20flag%20and%20remove%20inappropriate%2C%20offensive%20matter%2C%20largely%20because%20hate%20speech%20and%20incitement%20to%20violence%20is%20lucrative%20business.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EPracticing%20an%20unrestrained%20free%20speech%20absolutism%20where%20the%20hitherto%20unsayable%20is%20now%20par%20for%20the%20course%2C%20social%20media%20is%20dominated%20by%20a%20bewildering%20mix%20of%20right-wing%20nationalists%2C%20hatemongers%2C%20Islamophobic%20edgelords%20and%20Twitterati%20warriors%20who%20have%20corroded%20the%20entire%20system%20with%20the%20most%20unspeakable%2C%20venomous%20and%20divisive%20rhetoric%2C%20creating%20a%20dystopian%20world%20where%20there%20are%20no%20moral%20codes%20and%20where%20every%20fact%20is%20negotiable.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESocial%20media%20platforms%2C%20largely%20unmoderated%2C%20have%20become%20cesspools%20of%20toxic%20behaviour.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIt%20is%20frightening%20that%20social%20media%20has%20become%2C%20for%20most%20users%2C%20the%20sole%20fount%20of%20information%20and%20knowledge%20about%20the%20world%20around%20them.%20It%20gives%20them%20a%20false%20sense%20of%20power%20to%20avenge%20wrongs%20and%20punish%20enemies%2C%20while%20also%20providing%20them%20an%20outlet%20to%20vent%20their%20fears%20and%20insecurities.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWith%20its%20lethal%20arsenal%20of%20disinformation%2C%20alternative%20facts%2C%20violent%20trolling%2C%20doctored%20videos%2C%20odious%20propaganda%20%3Cem%3Eet%20al%3C%2Fem%3E%2C%20social%20media%20has%20seized%20absolute%20control%20in%20the%20%E2%80%9Cinformation%20war%E2%80%9D%2C%20even%20as%20the%20traditional%20media%20outlets%20shrink%20rapidly.%20The%20measured%2C%20thought-provoking%20op-eds%20have%20been%20supplanted%20by%20intellectually%20undemanding%20social%20media%20fare%2C%20a%20dumbing%20down%20that%20bodes%20ill%20for%20the%20future.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cins%3EAlso%20Read%3A%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fmedia%2Fbackstory-its-media-information-that-keeps-india-as-a-country-together-or-apart%5C%22%3EBackstory%3A%20It%E2%80%99s%20Media%20Information%20That%20Keeps%20India%20as%20a%20Country%20Together%20%E2%80%93%20or%20Apart%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fins%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIt%20is%20no%20accident%20that%20the%20weaponising%20of%20social%20media%20in%20the%20world%E2%80%99s%20two%20largest%20democracies%20coincided%20with%20the%20rise%20to%20power%20of%20Donald%20Trump%20and%20Narendra%20Modi%20%E2%80%93%20two%20leaders%20whose%20careers%20have%20been%20greatly%20influenced%2C%20if%20not%20defined%2C%20by%20their%20deep-rooted%2C%20visceral%20links%20with%20social%20media.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ETrump%20is%20universally%20recognised%20as%20the%20leading%20troll%20in%20the%20US.%20In%20July%202019%2C%20in%20the%20run-up%20to%20the%202020%20presidential%20elections%2C%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.nbcnews.com%2Fpolitics%2Fwhite-house%2Ftrump-touts-power-controversial-social-media-activists-white-house-summit-n1029036%5C%22%3Ehe%20convened%20a%20%E2%80%9Csocial%20media%20summit%E2%80%9D%20in%20the%20White%20House%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20inviting%20a%20gaggle%20of%20pro-Trump%20social%20media%20titans%20to%20strategise%20for%20the%20ensuing%20presidential%20elections.%20Social%20media%20constituted%20the%20main%20plank%20of%20his%20election%20strategy.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ENot%20renowned%20for%20his%20fidelity%20to%20the%20truth%2C%20Narendra%20Modi%E2%80%99s%20version%20of%20the%20role%20of%20social%20media%20is%20a%20stunning%20example%20of%20two-facedness.%20His%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2Fpmoindia%2Fstatus%2F647974165140533248%5C%22%3Estated%20position%3C%2Fa%3E%20is%20that%20%E2%80%9Csocial%20media%20is%20reducing%20social%20barriers.%20It%20connects%20people%20on%20the%20strength%20of%20human%20values%2C%20not%20identities%E2%80%9D.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBut%20the%20ugly%20reality%20is%20that%20he%20is%20a%20committed%20Hindu%20supremacist%2C%20whose%20camp%20followers%20have%20been%20persecuting%20Muslims%20and%20Christians%20amid%20electorally-inspired%20outreach%20targeting%20Pasmanda%20Muslims%20and%20a%20section%20of%20compromised%20Christian%20clergy%20%E2%80%93%20duplicitous%20gestures%20that%20fool%20nobody.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20her%20book%20%3Cem%3EI%20am%20a%20Troll%3C%2Fem%3E%2C%20intrepid%20journalist%20Swati%20Chaturvedi%20takes%20us%20into%20the%20dark%20recesses%20of%20the%20BJP%E2%80%99s%20social%20media%20world%2C%20whose%20main%20purpose%20is%20to%20purvey%20fake%20news%2C%20foment%20hatred%2C%20pillory%20opponents%2C%20empower%20bigotry%2C%20incite%20violence%20and%20undermine%20democracy.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EDespite%20being%20the%20target%20of%20the%20most%20scurrilous%20attacks%20by%20right-wing%20trolls%20and%20facing%20sustained%20harassment%20by%20the%20government%2C%20she%20stood%20her%20ground.%20She%20holds%20the%20PM%20responsible%20for%20emboldening%20them%3A%20%E2%80%9CI%E2%80%99ve%20been%20watching%20in%20horrified%20fascination%20as%20the%20leader%20of%20the%20world%E2%80%99s%20largest%20democracy%20follows%20and%20felicitates%20trolls.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cins%3EAlso%20Read%3A%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fpolitics%2Fnarendra-modi-twitter-trolls-free-expression%5C%22%3EGeneral%20Narendra%20Modi%20and%20His%20Troll%20Army%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fins%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWe%20live%20in%20an%20age%20of%20viral%20politics%2C%20where%20grassroots%20support%20is%20driven%20primarily%20by%20the%20internet%2C%20which%20is%20setting%20the%20agenda%20because%20of%20its%20omnipresence%20and%20unfiltered%20instant%20feedback.%20The%20days%20when%20voters%20took%20their%20cues%20from%20the%20studied%20analyses%20of%20the%20political%20pundits%20are%20over%2C%20as%20the%20vast%20majority%20turn%20to%20social%20media%20for%20determining%20their%20world%20view%20and%20certainly%20their%20electoral%20preference.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIndia%20and%20I.N.D.I.A%20had%20better%20watch%20out!%20The%202024%20general%20elections%20will%20be%20fought%20under%20the%20aegis%20of%20social%20media%2C%20which%20now%20occupies%20a%20central%20place%20in%20our%20democracy.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAnd%20it%20will%20not%20be%20a%20level%20playing%20field!%20As%20we%20head%20into%20the%20final%20lap%20of%20the%20election%20cycle%2C%20this%20dispensation%E2%80%99s%20troll%20armies%20will%20be%20going%20full%20tilt%20with%20their%20repertoire%20of%20dirty%20tricks%20%E2%80%93%20fake%20news%2C%20doctored%20videos%2C%20bigotry%2C%20polarising%20hate%2C%20incitement%20to%20violence.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWhile%20they%20have%20a%20free%20run%2C%20the%20surveillance%2C%20harassment%2C%20and%20curbs%20on%20the%20free%20speech%20of%20opponents%20and%20critics%20of%20the%20regime%20will%20be%20intensified.%20It%20is%20a%20formidable%20challenge%2C%20but%20how%20the%20Opposition%20and%20the%20people%20who%20care%20for%20democracy%20respond%20to%20the%20machinations%20of%20this%20dangerous%20outfit%20will%20determine%20the%20future%20of%20our%20democracy.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22http%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fauthor%2Fmathew-john%2F%5C%22%3EMathew%20John%3C%2Fa%3E%20is%20a%20former%20civil%20servant.%20Views%20are%20personal%3C%2Fem%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1691753434000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2022%2F04%2F13095447%2FIMG_0163.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fsociety%2Fa-cesspool-of-toxicity-occupies-a-central-place-in-our-democracy%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22The%202024%20general%20elections%20will%20be%20fought%20under%20the%20aegis%20of%20social%20media%2C%20which%20now%20occupies%20a%20central%20place%20in%20our%20democracy.%20And%20it%20will%20not%20be%20a%20level%20playing%20field.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A5%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fsociety%2Fa-cesspool-of-toxicity-occupies-a-central-place-in-our-democracy%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22CAG%20Finds%20Irregularities%20in%20Award%20of%20Highway%20Projects%20Under%20Bharatmala%20Pariyojana%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cimg%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2020%2F03%2F25192431%2FA-man-crosses-empty-NH24-whichnis-otherwisr-heavy-in-traffic-copy.jpg%5C%22%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3ENew%20Delhi%3A%3C%2Fstrong%3E%20The%20Comptroller%20and%20Auditor%20General%20(CAG)%20of%20India%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcag.gov.in%2Fen%2Faudit-report%2Fdetails%2F119177%5C%22%3Ehas%20found%3C%2Fa%3E%20instances%20of%20irregularities%20in%20the%20award%20of%20the%20Union%20government%E2%80%99s%20Bharatmala%20highway%20projects.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20audit%20%E2%80%93%20which%20covered%20the%20period%20from%202017-18%20to%202020-21%20%E2%80%93%20examines%20planning%2C%20financial%20management%2C%20implementation%2C%20and%3Cbr%3E%5Cnmonitoring%20of%2066%20sampled%20projects%20being%20implemented%20under%20Phase-I%20of%20Bharatmala%20Pariyojana.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20CAG%20report%20revealed%20instances%20of%20irregularities%20in%20the%20allocation%20of%20projects%20by%20implementing%20agencies%2C%20in%20violation%20of%20tendering%20protocols.%20For%20instance%2C%20in%20some%20cases%2C%20the%20successful%20bidder%20did%20not%20fulfill%20the%20tendering%20condition%20or%20the%20bidder%20was%20selected%20on%20the%20basis%20of%20falsified%20documents.%20Works%20were%20awarded%20in%20the%20absence%20of%20detailed%20project%20reports%2C%20or%20there%20were%20faulty%20project%20reports.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAccording%20to%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Findia%2Fcag-flags-bharatmala-bidding-irregularities%2Farticleshow%2F102625792.cms%3Ffrom%3Dmdr%5C%22%3Ethe%20%3Cem%3ETimes%20of%20India%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20the%20implementing%20agencies%20were%20awarding%20projects%20without%20ensuring%20availability%20of%20required%20land%20and%20forest%20clearance%2C%20which%20are%20resulting%20in%20delayed%20commencement%20and%20completion%20of%20projects.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20National%20Highways%20Authority%20of%20India%20and%20National%20Highways%20and%20Infrastructure%20Development%20Corporation%20Limited%20are%20the%20implementing%20agencies.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20CAG%20also%20found%20deficiencies%20in%20the%20appraisal%20and%20approval%20mechanism%20proposed%20to%20the%20Cabinet%20Committee%20on%20Economic%20Affairs%20(CCEA)%20in%20many%20of%20the%20high%20cost%20Engineering%20Procurement%20and%20Construction%20(EPC)%20projects%20or%20fully%20funded%20government%20projects.%20The%20Delhi-Vadodara%20Expressway%20and%20Dwarka%20Expressway%20could%20not%20be%20assessed%20either%20by%20the%20CCEA%20or%20the%20highways%20ministry%20to%20be%20scrutinised%20at%20that%20level.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CEven%20the%20appraisal%20and%20approval%20mechanism%20decided%20by%20CCEA%20was%20also%20not%20strictly%20followed%2C%E2%80%9D%20the%20CAG%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20CAG%20pointed%20out%20that%20there%20were%20significant%20cost%20overruns.%20It%20noted%20that%20only%2075.62%25%20of%20CCEA%20approved%20length%20has%20been%20awarded%20while%20158.24%25%20of%20approved%20financial%20outlay%20was%20sanctioned%20up%20to%20March%2031%2C%202023.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Phase-I%20of%20Bharatmala%20Pariyojana%20was%20for%20development%20up%20to%20September%202022%2C%20at%20an%20investment%20outlay%20of%20Rs%205%2C35%2C000%20crore.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3EThe%20Economic%20Times%3C%2Fem%3E%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Feconomictimes.indiatimes.com%2Fnews%2Feconomy%2Finfrastructure%2Fcag-flags-irregularities-in-bharatmala-project-tenders%2Farticleshow%2F102617116.cms%3Ffrom%3Dmdr%5C%22%3Ereported%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20citing%20the%20CAG%20report%2C%20that%20significant%20changes%20made%20in%20the%20scope%20of%20projects%20and%20cost%20estimates%20as%20well%20as%20richer%20project%20specifications%20adopted%20have%20pushed%20up%20the%20sanctioned%20cost%20of%20projects.%20%E2%80%9CThis%20has%20resulted%20in%20sanctioned%20civil%20cost%20being%20Rs%2023.89%20crore%20per%20kilometre%20(km)%20as%20against%20the%20CCEA%20approved%20cost%20of%20Rs%2013.98%20crore%20per%20km%20and%20sanctioned%20pre-construction%20cost%20being%20Rs%208.28%20crore%20per%20km%20as%20against%20the%20CCEA%20approved%20cost%20of%20Rs%201.39%20crore%20per%20km%2C%E2%80%9D%20the%20auditor%20noted.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20another%20report%2C%20the%20CAG%20found%20that%20NHAI%20continued%20to%20collect%20user%20fee%20in%20three%20toll%20plazas%20(namely%20Nathavalasa%2C%20Chalageri%2C%20Hebbalu%20in%20Southern%20India)%20during%20delayed%20period%20of%20construction.%20This%20was%20in%20violation%20of%20rules%20stating%20that%20no%20user%20fee%20shall%20be%20levied%20for%20the%20delayed%20period%2C%20leading%20to%20higher%20toll%20collection%20from%20commuters%2C%20the%20business%20daily%20reported.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1691752840000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2020%2F03%2F25192431%2FA-man-crosses-empty-NH24-whichnis-otherwisr-heavy-in-traffic-copy.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fgovernment%2Fcag-finds-irregularities-in-award-of-highway-projects-under-bharatmala-pariyojana%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22The%20CAG%20report%20found%20irregularities%20by%20implementing%20agencies%20in%20project%20allocation%2C%20violating%20tendering%20rules.%20This%20included%20cases%20where%20winning%20bidders%20didn't%20meet%20conditions%2C%20were%20chosen%20with%20fake%20documents%2C%20and%20projects%20were%20awarded%20without%20proper%20reports.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A136%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fgovernment%2Fcag-finds-irregularities-in-award-of-highway-projects-under-bharatmala-pariyojana%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Sobhita's%20gorgeous%20promotional%20looks%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%22%2C%22published%22%3A1691752080000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.toiimg.com%2Fphoto%2Fmsid-102647520%2Cimgsize-63062.cms%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Fentertainment%2Fhindi%2Fweb-stories%2Fsobhita-dhulipalas-gorgeous-looks-for-made-in-heaven-promotions%2Fphotostory%2F102647520.cms%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22%3Cimg%20border%3D%5C%220%5C%22%20align%3D%5C%22left%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Fphoto%2F102647520.cms%5C%22%20hspace%3D%5C%2210%5C%22%3E%E2%80%8BSobhita%20Dhulipala's%20gorgeous%20looks%20for%20'Made%20In%20Heaven'%20promotions!%20%E2%80%8B%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Fentertainment%2Fhindi%2Fweb-stories%2Fsobhita-dhulipalas-gorgeous-looks-for-made-in-heaven-promotions%2Fphotostory%2F102647520.cms%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Girl%20'dies%20from%20snake%20bite'%20in%20hut%20she%20was%