d%20why%20it%20was%20not%20being%20stopped%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cdiv%3E%3Ciframe%20allowfullscreen%3D%5C%22allowfullscreen%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fembed%2FeE4Pz1FJh9s%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%22100%25%5C%22%20title%3D%5C%22YouTube%20video%20player%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22504%5C%22%3E%3Cspan%20data-mce-type%3D%5C%22bookmark%5C%22%3E%EF%BB%BF%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fiframe%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EGandhi%20said%20his%20remarks%20that%20Prime%20Minister%20Modi%20and%20home%20minister%20Amit%20Shah%20had%20%E2%80%9C%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fgovernment%2Frahul-gandhi-parliament-bharat-mata-manipur%5C%22%3Emurdered%20Bharat%20Mata%20in%20Manipur%3C%2Fa%3E%E2%80%9D%20were%20not%20hollow.%20%E2%80%9CHindustan%20has%20been%20murdered%20by%20BJP%20in%20Manipur%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CWhen%20a%20person%20becomes%20PM%2C%20he%20should%20not%20speak%20like%20a%20petty%20politician.%20It%E2%80%99s%20tragic%20to%20watch%20PM%20Modi%20speak%20for%202%20hours%20on%20the%20Congress%2C%20opposition.%20It%20doesn%E2%80%99t%20do%20justice%20to%20his%20position%E2%80%A6%20The%20only%20conclusion%20I%20want%20to%20draw%20is%20that%20the%20PM%20has%20tools%20in%20hand%20but%20for%20some%20reasons%2C%20he%20refuses%20to%20use%20them.%20There%20are%20clear%20reasons%20why%20PM%20is%20not%20going%20to%20Manipur%2C%E2%80%9D%20Gandhi%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHe%20said%20the%20Army%20can%20bring%20peace%20in%202-3%20days%20but%20the%20government%20was%20not%20deploying%20it.%20%E2%80%9CI%20am%20not%20seeking%20Army%E2%80%99s%20intervention.%20All%20I%20am%20saying%20is%20that%20Army%20can%20stop%20this%20nonsense%20in%20two%20days.%20It%20is%20not%20my%20position%20to%20say%20which%20tool%20PM%20Modi%20will%20use%E2%80%9D%20the%20Congress%20leader%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1691751340000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F08%2F11162020%2FScre