%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F08%2F11144042%2FScreenshot-2023-08-11-at-2.27.23-PM_cleanup.png%5C%22%3E%3Cp%3EI%E2%80%99ve%20often%20wondered%20why%20competent%20Indian%20actors%20make%20the%20trip%20halfway%20around%20the%20world%2C%20only%20to%20be%20disrespected%20with%20the%20most%20perfunctory%20roles.%20%E2%80%9CIt%E2%80%99s%20a%20bigger%20profile%E2%80%9D%2C%20%E2%80%9CYou%E2%80%99ll%20work%20alongside%20Hollywood%20A-listers%E2%80%9D%2C%20%E2%80%9CIt%E2%80%99s%20a%20great%20career%20move%E2%80%9D%20%E2%80%93%20are%20often%20reasons%20that%20spring%20to%20mind.%20But%20then%20I%20realised%20how%20a%20year%20before%20her%20Hollywood%20debut%20in%20Netflix%E2%80%99s%20%3Cem%3EHeart%20of%20Stone%3C%2Fem%3E%2C%20Alia%20Bhatt%20played%20a%20similarly%20inane%20role%20in%20%3Cem%3EBrahmastra%3A%20Part%20One%20%E2%80%93%20Shiva%3C%2Fem%3E.%20Greed%2C%20I%20suppose%2C%20can%20convince%20the%20most%20lucid%20amongst%20us%20to%20participate%20in%20the%20most%20dim-witted%20enterprises%20in%20India%20and%20also%20across%20international%20borders.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWhat%20Bhatt%20%E2%80%93%20one%20of%20India%E2%80%99s%20most%20promising%20actors%20%E2%80%93%20has%20to%20suffer%20from%20in%20this%20Tom%20Harper%20film%20is%20nothing%20short%20of%20indignity.%20Playing%20the%20role%20of%20a%2022-year-old%20whizkid%20hacker%20named%20Keya%20Dhawan%2C%20Bhatt%20is%20mostly%20required%20to%20flash%20her%20luminous%20smile%20after%20delivering%20a%20snappy%20one-liner.%20And%20then%20feign%20surprise%20during%20the%20most%20basic%20plot-points%20of%20the%20film.%20%E2%80%9CYou%20told%20me%20you%20wanted%20to%20bring%20down%20the%20Charter%2C%20not%20kill%20the%20people%20running%20it%2C%E2%80%9D%20she%20shrieks%20at%20someone.%20Bhatt%2C%20who%20rose%20through%20the%20ranks%20of%20Bollywood%20by%20subverting%20ing%C3%A9nue%20parts%20with%20her%20spunk%2C%20is%20tasked%20with%20playing%20the%20outline%20of%20an%20ing%C3%A9nue%20here.%20To%20be%20fair%2C%20she%E2%80%99s%20sincere%20through%20most%20of%20it.%20It%E2%80%99s%20the%20film%20that%20is%20the%20bigger%20problem.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3EHeart%20of%20Stone%3C%2Fem%3E%20follows%20a%20secret%20spy%20outfit%20called%20the%20Charter%20%E2%80%93%20a%20body%20of%20international%20spies%20%E2%80%93%20which%20operates%20from%20the%20shadows.%20When%20international%20incidents%20get%20out%20of%20hand%2C%20the%20Charter%20intervenes.%20They%E2%80%99re%20guided%20by%20some%20supercomputer%20called%20the%20Heart%2C%20which%20can%20hack%20into%20any%20system%20in%20any%20part%20of%20the%20world%20thereby%20giving%20it%20absolute%20power%20in%20an%20increasingly%20digital%20world.%20It%20sounds%20eerily%20similar%20to%20the%20plot%20of%20%3Cem%3EMission%20Impossible%3A%20Dead%20Reckoning%20%E2%80%93%20Part%20One%3C%2Fem%3E%2C%20where%20Cruise%20and%20his%20colleagues%20chase%20a%20programme%20called%20The%20Entity.%20The%20only%20difference%20here%20is%20that%20the%20Heart%20doesn%E2%80%99t%20seem%20to%20be%20sentient%20yet.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ERachel%20Stone%20(Gal%20Gadot)%20is%20a%20devoted%20member%20of%20the%20Charter%2C%20with%20a%20vague%20and%20generic%20past.%20She%20pulls%20off%20daredevil%20stunts%2C%20has%20the%20odd%20sentimental%20moment%20of%20reflection%2C%20but%20a%20big%20part%20of%20her%20job%20is%20to%20get%20on%20the%20radio%20only%20to%20say%20%E2%80%9CI%E2%80%99m%20fine%E2%80%9D%20after%20escaping%20near-certain%20death%20yet%20again.%20There%E2%80%99s%20little%20doubt%20about%20Gadot%E2%80%99s%20prowess%20as%20an%20action%20star%20%E2%80%93%20but%20after%20%3Cem%3EWonder%20Woman%3C%2Fem%3E%20(2017)%2C%20each%20successive%20project%20of%20hers%20has%20chipped%20away%20at%20her%20credibility%20as%20even%20a%20barebones%20actor.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-caption%5C%22%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%20709px)%2085vw%2C%20(max-width%3A%20909px)%2067vw%2C%20(max-width%3A%201362px)%2062vw%2C%20840px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F08%2F11143259%2FScreenshot-2023-08-11-at-2.31.00-PM.jpg%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%221080%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F08%2F11143259%2FScreenshot-2023-08-11-at-2.31.00-PM.jpg%201080w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F08%2F11143259%2FScreenshot-2023-08-11-at-2.31.00-PM-300x229.jpg%20300w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F08%2F11143259%2FScreenshot-2023-08-11-at-2.31.00-PM-1024x783.jpg%201024w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-667660%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22826%5C%22%3E%3Cp%20class%3D%5C%22wp-caption-text%5C%22%3EGal%20Gadot%20in%20Heart%20of%20Stone%20(2023).%20Photo%3A%20Screengrab%20from%20video.%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOne%20of%20the%20biggest%20issues%20with%20%3Cem%3EHeart%20of%20Stone%3C%2Fem%3E%20is%20how%20little%20of%20it%20seems%20to%20have%20a%20voice%20of%20its%20own.%20The%20Charter%20seems%20to%20be%20borrowing%20from%20the%20age-old%20trope%20of%20secret%20societies%20of%20assassins%2Fspies%20%E2%80%93%20something%20that%20was%20recently%20rehashed%20in%20the%20Amazon%20original%2C%20Citadel.%20A%20machine%20dictating%20missions%2C%20as%20the%20world%E2%80%99s%20most%20highly-trained%20spies%20simply%20take%20its%20word%20without%20exercising%20their%20own%20discretion%2C%20is%20reminiscent%20of%20everything%20from%20Minority%20Report%20(2002)%20to%20Wanted%20(2008).%20The%20plot%20line%20of%20a%20former%20spy%20abandoned%20by%20his%20agency%2C%20coming%20back%20to%20get%20his%20revenge%2C%20is%20a%20trope%20that%20has%20been%20around%20forever%2C%20most%20prominently%20in%20Skyfall%20(2012).%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESomehow%2C%20it%E2%80%99s%20considered%20acceptable%20that%20one%20organisation%20wields%20the%20power%20of%20the%20Heart%2C%20and%20thereby%20make%20the%20calls%20for%20the%20%E2%80%98greater%20good%E2%80%99.%20It%E2%80%99s%20something%20even%20Tom%20Cruise%20struggles%20with%20in%20the%20latest%20Mission%20Impossible%20film.%20Therefore%2C%20it%E2%80%99s%20no%20surprise%20that%20the%20villains%20in%20this%20film%20(ably%20supported%20by%20Bhatt%E2%80%99s%20baby-faced%20hacker)%20will%20try%20and%20steal%20the%20Heart.%20Gadot%20must%20stop%20them.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EEven%20in%20a%20plot%20as%20superficial%20as%20this%20though%2C%20there%20might%20still%20be%20room%20for%20fun.%20A%20few%20imaginative%20action%20set-pieces%2C%20some%20unexpected%20humour%2C%20at%20least%20some%20personality%20to%20the%20characters%20beyond%20their%20cursory%20outline.%20Alas%2C%20%3Cem%3EHeart%20of%20Stone%3C%2Fem%3E%20is%20a%20testament%20to%20the%20Netflix%20assembly-line%20of%20action%20films%20%E2%80%93%20most%20of%20which%20seem%20to%20have%20the%20same%20bluish%20tinge%2C%20the%20action%20choreography%20seems%20to%20mistake%20loudness%20for%20scale%2C%20and%20the%20one-liners%20seem%20to%20have%20the%20smugness%20of%20a%20Marvel%20superhero%20film.%20It%20won%E2%80%99t%20be%20harsh%20to%20say%20that%20Heart%20of%20Stone%20feels%20like%20a%20microwaved%20version%20of%20all%20leftover%20tropes%20from%20action%20films%20from%20the%20past%20decade%20or%20so.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EFor%20a%20film%20that%20is%20hinged%20on%20a%20futuristic%20technology%20like%20an%20AI%2C%20%3Cem%3EHeart%20of%20Stone%3C%2Fem%3E%20feels%20weirdly%20dated.%20A%20lot%20of%20the%20frantic%20%E2%80%98hacking%20scenes%E2%80%99%20seem%20reminiscent%20of%20giddy%20%E2%80%9890s%20action%20films%20that%20usually%20employed%20a%20%E2%80%98hacker%E2%80%99%20to%20conjure%20all%20the%20contrivances%20a%20screenwriter%20could%20think%20of.%20Solid%20actors%20like%20Sophie%20Okonedo%20and%20Jamie%20Dornan%20are%20wasted%20in%20roles%20needing%20them%20to%20rally%20around%20Gadot%20%E2%80%93%20so%20that%20she%20can%20have%20her%20own%20action%20franchise%20moment.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAn%20unintentionally%20funny%20thing%20about%20Harper%E2%80%99s%20film%20is%20that%20a%20billion-dollar%20corporation%20leads%20with%20knowing%20Bhatt%E2%80%99s%20potential%2C%20and%20then%20goes%20on%20to%20confidently%20waste%20her%20talents.%20They%E2%80%99re%20clueless%2C%20just%20like%20in%20the%20matters%20of%20the%20heart.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1691746240000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F08%2F11144042%2FScreenshot-2023-08-11-at-2.27.23-PM_cleanup.png%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Ffilm%2Fheart-of-stone-alia-bhatts-lifeless-hollywood-debut-in-a-tired-cliched-spy-movie%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22The%20Netflix%20formula%20for%20action%20films%20is%20resolutely%20stuck%20in%20the%20past%2C%20churning%20out%20the%20same%20old%20set%20pieces.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A29%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Ffilm%2Fheart-of-stone-alia-bhatts-lifeless-hollywood-debut-in-a-tired-cliched-spy-movie%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Australia%20considers%20bidding%20for%20men's%20World%20Cup%20after%20'happy'%20experience%20hosting%20women's%20event%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%22%2C%22published%22%3A1691745600000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fe3.365dm.com%2F23%2F08%2F768x432%2Fskynews-world-cup-spain-netherlands_6247303.jpg%3F20230811104428%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fnews.sky.com%2Fstory%2Faustralia-considers-bidding-for-mens-world-cup-after-happy-experience-hosting-womens-event-12937802%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Australia%20is%20exploring%20a%20bid%20for%20the%202034%20Men's%20World%20Cup%20%E2%80%93%20buoyed%20by%20FIFA's%20praise%20of%20its%20co-hosting%20of%20the%20women's%20event.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A167%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fnews.sky.com%2Fstory%2Faustralia-considers-bidding-for-mens-world-cup-after-happy-experience-hosting-womens-event-12937802%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fnews-sky-com.cdn.ampproject.org%2Fc%2Fs%2Fnews.sky.com%2Fstory%2Famp%2Faustralia-considers-bidding-for-mens-world-cup-after-happy-experience-hosting-womens-event-12937802%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fnews.sky.com%2Fstory%2Famp%2Faustralia-considers-bidding-for-mens-world-cup-after-happy-experience-hosting-womens-event-12937802%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Manipur%20Has%20Been%20Without%20Internet%20Services%20for%20100%20Days%20Now%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cimg%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F08%2F09095437%2FWhatsApp-Image-2023-08-08-at-12.01.44-PM.jpeg%5C%22%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3ENew%20Delhi%3A%C2%A0%3C%2Fstrong%3EAugust%2011%20marks%20100%20days%20since%20ethnic%20violence%20broke%20out%20in%20Manipur%20%E2%80%93%20and%20100%20days%20since%20the%20state%20government%20first%20shut%20down%20the%20internet.%20The%20high%20court%20has%20ordered%20a%20%E2%80%9Cpartial%20restoration%E2%80%9D%20of%20internet%20services%20%E2%80%93%20but%2C%20as%20experts%20have%20pointed%20out%2C%20that%20partial%20restoration%20meets%20the%20needs%20only%20of%20a%20very%20small%20proportion%20of%20the%20state%E2%80%99s%20population.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Internet%20Freedom%20Foundation%20has%20issued%20a%20statement%20condemning%20the%20ongoing%20internet%20shutdown%2C%20saying%20that%20%E2%80%9Cthe%20citizens%20of%20Manipur%20are%20being%20deprived%20of%20their%20basic%20human%20rights%E2%80%9D.%20The%20research%20and%20advocacy%20organisation%20has%20also%20argued%20that%20the%20shutdown%20is%20in%20fact%20breeding%20misinformation%2C%20and%20people%20are%20being%20unable%20to%20independently%20verify%20what%20they%20hear.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ERead%20the%20full%20statement%20below.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%C2%A7%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E100%20Days.%20Today%2C%20August%2011%2C%202023%2C%20marks%20100%20days%20of%20Manipur%E2%80%99s%20descent%20into%20a%20state-wide%20internet%20shutdown.%20We%2C%20at%20IFF%2C%20are%20deeply%20saddened%20and%20perturbed%20by%20the%20state%20of%20affairs%20and%20how%20the%20citizens%20of%20Manipur%20are%20being%20deprived%20of%20their%20basic%20human%20rights.%20It%20contributes%20to%20the%20propagation%20of%20misinformation%20without%20any%20means%20for%20verification%20and%20hinders%20the%20accountability%20process%20for%20human%20rights%20violations.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20suspension%20of%20internet%20access%2C%20which%20was%20imposed%20on%20May%203%2C%202023%2C%20was%20narrowly%20lifted%20on%20July%2025%2C%202023%2C%20only%20in%20the%20case%20of%20broadband%20services%20(internet%20leased%20line%20and%20fibre%20to%20the%20home)%2C%20even%20though%20broadband%20constitutes%20just%203%25%20of%20all%20internet%20connections%20in%20India.%20What%20is%20quite%20alarming%20is%20the%20absence%20of%20an%20end%20date%20in%20the%20July%2025%20order%20which%20effectively%20makes%20the%20suspension%20indefinite%20in%20nature.%20This%20makes%20the%20order%C2%A0%3Cem%3Eprima%20facie%C2%A0%3C%2Fem%3Eillegal%20as%20it%20violates%20Rule%202(2A)%20of%20the%20Telecom%20Suspension%2C%202017%2C%20as%20amended%20in%202020%2C%20after%20the%20Supreme%20Court%20in%C2%A0%3Cem%3EAnuradha%20Bhasin%20v.%20Union%20of%20India%C2%A0%3C%2Fem%3Enoted%20that%20any%20restrictions%20on%20internet%20services%20must%20be%20temporally%20and%20geographically%20limited.%20Rule%202(2A)%20states%20that%20no%20internet%20suspension%20order%20shall%20be%20in%20operation%20for%20more%20than%20fifteen%20days.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EFurther%2C%20this%20partial%20restoration%20of%20internet%20services%20comes%20attached%20with%20several%20conditions%2C%20and%20mobile%20data%20services%20remain%20suspended.%20ISPs%20have%20been%20directed%20to%20ensure%20the%20continued%20blocking%20of%20social%20media%20websites%20and%20VPNs%20at%20the%20local%20level%20even%20for%20broadband%20users.%20Physical%20monitoring%20for%20checking%20violation%20of%20terms%20and%20conditions%20may%20also%20be%20undertaken%20by%20the%20law%20enforcement%20authorities.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EA%20vast%20majority%20of%20the%20residents%20of%20Manipur%20remain%20without%20any%20access%20to%20the%20internet%2C%20and%20such%20disproportionate%20terms%20and%20conditions%20cannot%20be%20considered%20to%20be%20the%20least%20restrictive%20measure%20as%20per%20the%20doctrine%20of%20proportionality%20propounded%20in%C2%A0%3Cem%3EAnuradha%20Bhasin%20v.%20Union%20of%20India%3C%2Fem%3E.%20Access%20to%20healthcare%2C%20education%2C%20banking%20facilities%2C%20and%20livelihood%2C%20are%20all%20impacted.%20The%20economy%20also%20suffers%20drastically.%20Access%20to%20government%20welfare%20schemes%2C%20which%20are%20dependent%20on%20the%20internet%2C%20is%20also%20impeded.%20For%20instance%2C%20a%20joint%20report%20by%20Human%20Rights%20Watch%20and%20IFF%20on%20the%20human%20impact%20of%20internet%20shutdowns%20documented%20how%20workers%20dependent%20on%20rural%20employment%20guarantee%20schemes%2C%20lost%20wages%20as%20they%20were%20unable%20to%20mark%20their%20attendance%20on%20a%20government%20app%20due%20to%20internet%20suspension.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20only%20procedural%20safeguard%20afforded%20by%20the%20Telecom%20Suspension%20Rules%20against%20internet%20shutdowns%20is%20in%20the%20form%20of%20a%20Review%20Committee%2C%20headed%20by%20the%20State%E2%80%99s%20Chief%20Secretary%2C%20which%20must%20meet%20and%20determine%20the%20legality%20of%20the%20internet%20shutdown%20orders.%20Disappointingly%2C%20there%20is%20no%20record%20of%20Manipur%E2%80%99s%20Review%20Committee%20ever%20meeting%20or%20considering%20even%20one%20of%20the%20several%20subsequent%20internet%20shutdown%20orders%20that%20have%20been%20routinely%20passed%20by%20the%20Home%20Department%20of%20the%20Manipur%20Government.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMoreover%2C%20in%20the%20past%20few%20weeks%2C%20a%20bone-chilling%20video%20has%20emerged%20from%20Manipur%20that%20has%20shattered%20the%20apathy%20and%20silence%20surrounding%20the%20longest%20internet%20shutdown%20in%20the%20country%20in%202023.%20Action%20was%20taken%20against%20the%20perpetrators%20involved%20only%20after%20the%20video%20generated%20explosive%20anger%20across%20the%20public.%20This%20information%20blackhole%20caused%20by%20the%20internet%20shutdown%20has%20not%20only%20had%20a%20negative%20impact%20on%20individuals%E2%80%99%20right%20to%20access%20information%20and%20communicate%20freely%2C%20but%20has%20also%20obstructed%20people%20outside%20Manipur%20from%20being%20aware%20of%20the%20ground%20realities%20and%20violence%20that%20is%20taking%20place%20in%20the%20state.%20The%20consequent%20information%20disorder%20and%20absence%20of%20internet%20access%20also%20throttles%20voices%2C%20especially%20those%20of%20marginalised%20communities%2C%20and%20takes%20away%20their%20ability%20to%20document%20the%20violations%20they%20have%20faced.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThese%20egregious%20violations%20of%20human%20rights%20and%20the%20shocking%20contempt%20for%20Supreme%20Court%E2%80%99s%20ruling%20in%C2%A0%3Cem%3EAnuradha%20Bhasin%20v.%20Union%20of%20India%3C%2Fem%3E%C2%A0are%20concerning.%20It%20reveals%20a%20pattern%20of%20paternalistic%20governance%20transpiring%20in%20the%20country%20while%20attempting%20to%20obscure%20the%20government%E2%80%99s%20failures%20in%20preventing%20law%20and%20order%20problems.%20In%20such%20dark%20times%2C%20IFF%20expresses%20its%20unwavering%20support%20for%20the%20victims%20and%20reaffirms%20its%20dedication%20to%20championing%20the%20defence%20of%20digital%20rights%20as%20well%20the%20ethical%20utilisation%20of%20technology.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1691745319000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F08%2F09095437%2FWhatsApp-Image-2023-08-08-at-12.01.44-PM.jpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Frights%2Fmanipur-has-been-without-internet-services-for-100-days-now%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22The%20shutdown%20%26quot%3Bcontributes%20to%20the%20propagation%20of%20misinformation%20without%20any%20means%20for%20verification%20and%20hinders%20the%20accountability%20process%20for%20human%20rights%20violations%2C%26quot%3B%20the%20Internet%20Freedom%20Foundation%20has%20said.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A43%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Frights%2Fmanipur-has-been-without-internet-services-for-100-days-now%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22%E2%80%98Religion%20and%20Government%20Have%20No%20Connection%E2%80%99%3A%20Karnataka%20CM%20Siddaramaiah%20to%20Top%20Officials%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cimg%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F05%2F18164526%2FFwBN2HcakAEGvBw.jpeg%5C%22%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3ENew%20Delhi%3A%3C%2Fstrong%3E%20Karnataka%20chief%20minister%20Siddaramaiah%20on%20Wednesday%20urged%20government%20officials%20to%20carry%20out%20their%20duties%20without%20letting%20their%20religious%20affiliations%20cloud%20their%20judgement%20and%20to%20uphold%20secularism%20in%20their%20conduct%2C%20the%20%3Cem%3ETelegraph%3C%2Fem%3E%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.telegraphindia.com%2Findia%2Fgovernment-officials-should-not-intervene-in-political-matters-and-religious-issues-siddaramaiah%2Fcid%2F1958155%5C%22%3Ereported%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESiddaramaiah%20was%20addressing%20centenary%20celebrations%20of%20the%20Karnataka%20Administration%20Services%20Association%20in%20Bangalore.%20%E2%80%9CReligion%20exists.%20But%20religion%20and%20government%20have%20no%20connection%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20was%20quoted%20by%20the%20paper%20as%20saying.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CGovernment%20officials%20should%20not%20intervene%20in%20political%20matters%20and%20religious%20issues.%20Our%20Constitution%20has%20made%20this%20very%20clear.%20It%20(the%20Constitution)%20very%20clearly%20upholds%20secularism%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20added.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHis%20strongly%20worded%20advice%20is%20in%20line%20with%20the%20Congress%20government%E2%80%99s%20efforts%20to%20cleanse%20the%20bureaucracy%2C%20sections%20of%20which%20the%20party%20had%20accused%20of%20becoming%20a%20tool%20in%20the%20hands%20of%20the%20previous%20BJP%20dispensation%2C%20the%20%3Cem%3ETelegraph%3C%2Fem%3E%20report%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESiddaramaiah%20and%20his%20deputy%20D.K.%20Shivakumar%20had%20also%20warned%20the%20state%E2%80%99s%20top%20police%20officials%20against%20saffronisation.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAt%20the%20centenary%20event%2C%20the%20Karnataka%20chief%20asked%20officials%20to%20work%20within%20the%20framework%20of%20the%20Constitution%2C%20adding%20that%20it%20is%20everyone%E2%80%99s%20responsibility%20to%20protect%20it.%20%E2%80%9CIf%20you%20protect%20the%20Constitution%2C%20the%20Constitution%20will%20protect%20all%20of%20us%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20was%20quoted%20by%20the%20%3Cem%3ETelegraph%3C%2Fem%3E%20as%20saying.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CThe%20educated%20should%20be%20rational%20(human%20beings)%20and%20not%20be%20advocates%20of%20the%20caste%20system.%20Only%20then%20can%20we%20bring%20about%20changes%20in%20society%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20noted.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESiddaramaiah%20has%20carried%20forward%20the%20cause%20of%20Ahindas%20for%20social%20justice%20%E2%80%93%20a%20concept%20developed%20by%20Congress%20leader%20and%20then%20chief%20minister%20Devraj%20Urs%20in%20the%20early%201970s%20and%20has%20had%20socialist%20leanings%20since%20he%20was%20a%20student%2C%20the%20Telegraph%20report%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CIntrospect%20your%20responsibilities.%20While%20it%20is%20we%2C%20the%20politicians%2C%20who%20frame%20laws%2C%20you%20are%20the%20ones%20who%20implement%20them%20as%20you%20work%20between%20the%20people%20and%20the%20government.%20If%20you%20work%20for%20the%20people%2C%20even%20we%20earn%20a%20good%20image%2C%E2%80%9D%20Siddaramaiah%20was%20quoted%20by%20the%20%3Cem%3ETelegraph%3C%2Fem%3E%20as%20saying.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CThere%20are%20lots%20of%20good%20government%20servants.%20But%20there%20are%20some%20who%20are%20not.%20Under%20no%20circumstances%20should%20you%20engage%20in%20anti-people%20and%20anti-farmer%20activities%2C%E2%80%9D%20the%20chief%20minister%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1691744449000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F05%2F18164526%2FFwBN2HcakAEGvBw.jpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fgovernment%2Freligion-and-government-have-no-connection-karnataka-cm-siddaramaiah-to-top-officials%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22He%20urged%20government%20officials%20to%20carry%20out%20their%20duties%20without%20letting%20their%20religious%20affiliations%20cloud%20their%20judgement.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A35%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fgovernment%2Freligion-and-government-have-no-connection-karnataka-cm-siddaramaiah-to-top-officials%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%2242%20SITs%2C%20Overseeing%20Officers%20from%20Other%20States%3A%20What%20the%20SC%20Order%20on%20Manipur%20Violence%20Calls%20For%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cimg%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F08%2F11142639%2FUntitled-design-1-1.jpg%5C%22%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3ENew%20Delhi%3A%3C%2Fstrong%3E%20In%20its%20order%20on%20August%207%20%E2%80%93%20through%20which%20the%20Supreme%20Court%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Flaw%2Fmanipur-violence-sc-judicial-commission-examine-probes-remedial-measures%5C%22%3Econstituted%3C%2Fa%3E%20a%20committee%20of%20three%20woman%20judges%20of%20high%20courts%20to%20look%20into%20the%20humanitarian%20aspects%20of%20the%20ethnic%20violence%20in%20Manipur%20%E2%80%93%20the%20division%20bench%20also%20issued%20a%20number%20of%20directions.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20directions%20came%20after%20a%20bench%20comprising%20Chief%20Justice%20of%20India%20D.Y.%20Chandrachud%2C%20Justice%20J.B.%20Pardiwala%20and%20Justice%20Manoj%20Misra%20heard%20several%20petitions%20on%20the%20Manipur%20violence.%20Among%20the%20petitioners%20were%20two%20women%20from%20the%20Kuki-Zomi%20community%20who%20were%C2%A0%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fwomen%2Fmanipur-5-policemen-suspended-over-viral-video-of-sexual-assault%5C%22%3Eparaded%20naked%3C%2Fa%3E%20and%20sexually%20assaulted%20by%20a%20mob.%20The%20court%20has%20earlier%20been%20critical%20of%20the%20governments%E2%80%99%20handling%20of%20the%20violence%2C%20which%20has%20gone%20on%20for%20over%20three%20months%2C%20led%20to%20the%20death%20of%20150%20people%20and%20to%20tens%20of%20thousands%20being%20displaced.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOn%20August%201%2C%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Flaw%2Fsupreme-court-manipur-violence-police%5C%22%3Eit%20had%20called%20police%20investigation%20%E2%80%9Ctardy%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fa%3E%20and%20asked%20Manipur%E2%80%99s%20Director%20General%20of%20Police%20to%20be%20present%20in%20court%20to%20be%20able%20to%20answer%20judges.%20In%20its%20August%207%20judgment%2C%20the%20court%20has%20repeated%20the%20word%20%E2%80%9Ctardy.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CThere%20has%20been%20a%20considerable%20lapse%20between%20the%20occurrence%20and%20the%20registration%20of%20FIRs%2C%20recording%20of%20witness%20statements%20and%20even%20the%20arrests%20are%20few%20and%20far%20between%2C%E2%80%9D%20the%20bench%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3ESupervision%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20its%20August%207%20order%2C%20bench%20noted%20that%20the%20process%20of%20investigation%20by%20the%20Central%20Bureau%20of%20Investigation%20shall%20be%20monitored%20by%20the%20apex%20court.%20Former%20Maharashtra%20Director%20General%20of%20Police%2C%20Dattatray%20Padsalgikar%2C%20was%20appointed%20supervisor.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIt%20also%20directed%20the%20Union%20Ministry%20of%20Home%20Affairs%20to%20place%20at%20the%20disposal%20of%20the%20CBI%2C%20five%20Deputy%20Superintendent%20of%20Police-rank%20officers%20from%20Rajasthan%2C%20Madhya%20Pradesh%2C%20Jharkhand%2C%20Odisha%20and%20the%20Delhi%20National%20Capital%20Territory%2C%20at%20least%20one%20of%20whom%20is%20a%20woman.%20These%20officers%20will%20need%20to%20submit%20periodical%20information%20and%20reports%20to%20Padsalgikar.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20court%20also%20asked%20Padsalgikar%20to%20investigate%20the%20allegations%20that%20certain%20police%20officers%20colluded%20with%20perpetrators%20of%20violence%20(including%20sexual%20violence)%20during%20the%20conflict%20in%20Manipur%20and%20submit%20a%20report%20to%20the%20court.%20It%20directed%20the%20Union%20and%20Manipur%20governments%20to%20provide%20any%20assistance%20required%20in%20order%20to%20carry%20out%20this%20investigation.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20court%20ordered%20the%20formation%20of%20no%20fewer%20than%2042%20special%20investigation%20teams.%20One%2C%20headed%20by%20a%20superintendent-rank%20officer%20to%20look%20at%20FIRs%20related%20to%20murder%20and%20other%20heinous%20crimes%2C%20and%20another%2C%20including%20a%20female%20inspector%20for%20FIRs%20related%20to%20rape%2C%20outraging%20of%20modesty%20and%20such%20other%20sexual%20offences.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOther%20FIRs%20will%20be%20investigated%20by%20SITs%20headed%20by%20an%20officer%20not%20below%20the%20rank%20of%20deputy%20superintendent%20of%20police.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20court%20asked%20for%20six%20SITs%20for%20the%20districts%20of%20Churachandpur%2C%20Kangpokpi%2C%20Imphal%20West%2C%20Imphal%20East%2C%20Bishnupur%20and%20Kakching%2C%20and%20three%20for%20Thoubal%20and%20Tengnoupal%20districts.%20These%20SITs%20will%20be%20supervised%20weekly%20by%20an%20officer%20of%20the%20rank%20of%20deputy%20inspector%20general%20of%20police%2C%20inspector%20general%20of%20police%20or%20additional%20director%20general.%20In%20addition%2C%20the%20DGP%20will%20also%20monitor%20these%20cases%20fortnightly.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20apex%20court%20also%20said%20that%20in%20order%20to%20ensure%20proper%20monitoring%20and%20supervision%20of%20the%20investigation%20by%20the%20police%20authorities%2C%20the%20Union%20home%20ministry%20shall%20depute%20one%20officer%20of%20the%20rank%20of%20Police%20Inspector%20each%20from%20Rajasthan%2C%20Madhya%20Pradesh%2C%20Odisha%2C%20Jharkhand%2C%20Maharashtra%20and%20the%20NCT%20of%20Delhi.%20At%20least%2014%20officers%20not%20below%20the%20rank%20of%20superintendent%20of%20police%20are%20to%20be%20in%20charge%20of%20the%20respective%20SITs%2C%20said%20the%20Supreme%20Court.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESITs%20comprising%20women%20officers%20should%20be%20in%20charge%20of%20the%20investigation%20of%20crimes%20involving%20sexual%20violence.%20The%20court%20also%20mandated%20that%20SITs%20probing%20such%20violence%20stick%20to%20Supreme%20Court%20directions%20issued%20in%20%3Cem%3ENipun%20Saxena%20v.%20Union%20of%20India%20%3C%2Fem%3Eand%3Cem%3E%20XYZ%20v.%20State%20of%20Madhya%20Pradesh.%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Supreme%20Court%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Flaw%2Fwe-cant-justify-what-happened-in-manipur-by-saying-this-happened-elsewhere-sc%5C%22%3Eon%20July%2031%20had%20said%3C%2Fa%3E%20that%20the%20sexual%20violence%20incident%20in%20Manipur%20cannot%20be%20justified%20by%20saying%20that%20%E2%80%9Cthis%20and%20this%20happened%20elsewhere%E2%80%9D.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EStress%20on%20inclusion%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20apex%20court%20in%20its%20August%207%20order%20also%20said%20that%20each%20SIT%20will%20visit%20each%20relief%20camp%20within%20the%20area%20assigned%20to%20it%20and%20make%20it%20known%20that%20it%20is%20an%20impartial%20body%20which%20is%20accepting%20complaints%20of%20violence%2C%20including%20sexual%20violence.%20%E2%80%9CThis%20is%20necessary%20because%20many%20survivors%20%2F%20victims%20may%20not%20approach%20the%20police%20machinery%20of%20their%20own%20accord%2C%20especially%20in%20the%20aftermath%20of%20sectarian%20violence%20which%20may%20have%20resulted%20in%20the%20loss%20of%20family%20members%20and%20homes%2C%20displacement%2C%20and%20trauma%20to%20their%20own%20bodies%20and%20minds%2C%E2%80%9D%20the%20court%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ECrucially%2C%20the%20apex%20court%20also%20said%20that%20SITs%20constituted%20by%20Manipur%20government%20shall%20not%20consist%20exclusively%20of%20members%20belonging%20to%20either%20one%20of%20the%20communities%20involved%20in%20the%20clashes%20in%20the%20state.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20court%20also%20noted%20that%20the%20victims%20of%20violence%20must%20receive%20remedial%20measures%20irrespective%20of%20their%20community.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ELikewise%2C%20it%20said%2C%20the%20perpetrators%20of%20violence%20must%20be%20held%20accountable%20irrespective%20of%20the%20source%20of%20violence.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20bench%20also%20addressed%20widespread%20concerns%20over%20police%20having%20favoured%20one%20community%20over%20another.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CThere%20are%20serious%20allegations%20including%20witness%20statements%20indicating%20that%20the%20law-enforcing%20machinery%20has%20been%20inept%20in%20controlling%20the%20violence%20and%2C%20in%20certain%20situations%2C%20colluded%20with%20the%20perpetrators.%20Absent%20a%20proper%20investigation%2C%20this%20Court%20will%20not%20enter%20a%20finding%20of%20fact%20on%20these%20allegations.%20But%2C%20at%20the%20very%20least%2C%20such%20allegations%20require%20an%20objective%20fact-finding%20to%20be%20conducted%2C%E2%80%9D%20it%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThose%20who%20are%20responsible%20for%20a%20breach%20of%20public%20duty%20must%20equally%20be%20brought%20to%20account%2C%20regardless%20of%20their%20rank%2C%20position%2C%20or%20post%2C%20the%20order%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CEvery%20officer%20of%20the%20state%20or%20other%20employee%20of%20the%20state%20who%20is%20guilty%20not%20only%20of%20the%20dereliction%20of%20their%20constitutional%20and%20official%20duties%20but%20of%20colluding%20with%20perpetrators%20to%20become%20offenders%20themselves%2C%20must%20be%20held%20accountable%20without%20fail.%20This%20is%20the%20promise%20of%20justice%20that%20the%20Constitution%20demands%20from%20this%20Court%20and%20from%20all%20branches%20of%20the%20state%2C%E2%80%9D%20it%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1691744292000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F08%2F11142639%2FUntitled-design-1-1.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Flaw%2Fsupreme-court-manipur-violence-sit-sexual-crimes-murder%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22The%20apex%20court%20in%20its%20August%207%20order%20said%20that%20each%20SIT%20will%20visit%20each%20relief%20camp%20within%20the%20area%20assigned%20to%20it%20and%20make%20it%20known%20that%20it%20is%20an%20impartial%20body%20which%20is%20accepting%20complaints%20of%20violence%2C%20including%20sexual%20violence.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Flaw%2Fsupreme-court-manipur-violence-sit-sexual-crimes-murder%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%2242%20SITs%2C%20Overseeing%20Officers%20from%20Other%20States%3A%20What%20the%20SC%20Order%20on%20Manipur%20Violence%20Calls%20For%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cimg%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F08%2F11142639%2FUntitled-design-1-1.jpg%5C%22%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3ENew%20Delhi%3A%3C%2Fstrong%3E%20In%20its%20order%20on%20August%207%20%E2%80%93%20through%20which%20the%20Supreme%20Court%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Flaw%2Fmanipur-violence-sc-judicial-commission-examine-probes-remedial-measures%5C%22%3Econstituted%3C%2Fa%3E%20a%20committee%20of%20three%20woman%20judges%20of%20high%20courts%20to%20look%20into%20the%20humanitarian%20aspects%20of%20the%20ethnic%20violence%20in%20Manipur%20%E2%80%93%20the%20division%20bench%20also%20issued%20a%20number%20of%20directions.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20directions%20