ion%20Ministry%20of%20Home%20Affairs%20to%20place%20at%20the%20disposal%20of%20the%20CBI%2C%20five%20Deputy%20Superintendent%20of%20Police-rank%20officers%20from%20Rajasthan%2C%20Madhya%20Pradesh%2C%20Jharkhand%2C%20Odisha%20and%20the%20Delhi%20National%20Capital%20Territory%2C%20at%20least%20one%20of%20whom%20is%20a%20woman.%20These%20officers%20will%20need%20to%20submit%20periodical%20information%20and%20reports%20to%20Padsalgikar.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20court%20also%20asked%20Padsalgikar%20to%20investigate%20the%20allegations%20that%20certain%20police%20officers%20colluded%20with%20perpetrators%20of%20violence%20(including%20sexual%20violence)%20during%20the%20conflict%20in%20Manipur%20and%20submit%20a%20report%20to%20the%20court.%20It%20directed%20the%20Union%20and%20Manipur%20governments%20to%20provide%20any%20assistance%20required%20in%20order%20to%20carry%20out%20this%20investigation.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20court%20ordered%20the%20formation%20of%20no%20fewer%20than%2042%20special%20investigation%20teams.%20One%2C%20headed%20by%20a%20superintendent-rank%20officer%20to%20look%20at%20FIRs%20related%20to%20murder%20and%20other%20heinous%20crimes%2C%20and%20another%2C%20including%20a%20female%20inspector%20for%20FIRs%20related%20to%20rape%2C%20outraging%20of%20modesty%20and%20such%20other%20sexual%20offences.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOther%20FIRs%20will%20be%20investigated%20by%20SITs%20headed%20by%20an%20officer%20not%20below%20the%20rank%20of%20deputy%20superintendent%20of%20police.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20court%20asked%20for%20six%20SITs%20for%20the%20districts%20of%20Churachandpur%2C%20Kangpokpi%2C%20Imphal%20West%2C%20Imphal%20East%2C%20Bishnupur%20and%20Kakching%2C%20and%20three%20for%20Thoubal%20and%20Tengnoupal%20districts.%20These%20SITs%20will%20be%20supervised%20weekly%20by%20an%20officer%20of%20the%20rank%20of%20deputy%20inspector%20general%20of%20police%2C%20inspector%20general%20of%20police%20or%20additional%20director%20general.%20In%20addition%2