approach%20the%20police%20machinery%20of%20their%20own%20accord%2C%20especially%20in%20the%20aftermath%20of%20sectarian%20violence%20which%20may%20have%20resulted%20in%20the%20loss%20of%20family%20members%20and%20homes%2C%20displacement%2C%20and%20trauma%20to%20their%20own%20bodies%20and%20minds%2C%E2%80%9D%20the%20court%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ECrucially%2C%20the%20apex%20court%20also%20said%20that%20SITs%20constituted%20by%20Manipur%20government%20shall%20not%20consist%20exclusively%20of%20members%20belonging%20to%20either%20one%20of%20the%20communities%20involved%20in%20the%20clashes%20in%20the%20state.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20court%20also%20noted%20that%20the%20victims%20of%20violence%20must%20receive%20remedial%20measures%20irrespective%20of%20their%20community.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ELikewise%2C%20it%20said%2C%20the%20perpetrators%20of%20violence%20must%20be%20held%20accountable%20irrespective%20of%20the%20source%20of%20violence.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20bench%20also%20addressed%20widespread%20concerns%20over%20police%20having%20favoured%20one%20community%20over%20another.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CThere%20are%20serious%20allegations%20including%20witness%20statements%20indicating%20that%20the%20law-enforcing%20machinery%20has%20been%20inept%20in%20controlling%20the%20violence%20and%2C%20in%20certain%20situations%2C%20colluded%20with%20the%20perpetrators.%20Absent%20a%20proper%20investigation%2C%20this%20Court%20will%20not%20enter%20a%20finding%20of%20fact%20on%20these%20allegations.%20But%2C%20at%20the%20very%20least%2C%20such%20allegations%20require%20an%20objective%20fact-finding%20to%20be%20conducted%2C%E2%80%9D%20it%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThose%20who%20are%20responsible%20for%20a%20breach%20of%20public%20duty%20must%20equally%20be%20brought%20to%20account%2C%20regardless%20of%20their%20rank%2C%20position%2C%20or%20post%2C%20the%20order%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CEvery%20officer%20of%20the%20state%20or%20other%20employee%20of%20the%20state%20who%20is%20guilty%20not%20only%20of%20the%20dereliction%20of%20their%20constitutional%20and%20official%20duties%20but%20of%20colluding%20with%20perpetrators%20to%20become%20offenders%20themselves%2C%20must%20be%20held%20accountable%20without%20fail.%20This%20is%20the%20promise%20of%20justice%20that%20the%20Constitution%20demands%20from%20this%20Court%20and%20from%20all%20branches%20of%20the%20state%2C%E2%80%9D%20it%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1691744292000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F08%2F11142639%2FUntitled-design-1-1.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fcommunalism%2Fsupreme-court-manipur-violence-sit-sexual-crimes-murder%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22The%20apex%20court%20in%20its%20August%207%20order%20said%20that%20each%20SIT%20will%20visit%20each%20relief%20camp%20within%20the%20area%20assigned%20to%20it%20and%20make%20it%20known%20that%20it%20is%20an%20impartial%20body%20which%20is%20accepting%20complaints%20of%20violence%2C%20including%20sexual%20violence.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A9%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fcommunalism%2Fsupreme-court-manipur-violence-sit-sexual-crimes-murder%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Ukrainian%20drone%20jammed%20over%20Moscow%3A%20Russia%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%22%2C%22published%22%3A1691743611000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.toiimg.com%2Fphoto%2Fmsid-102642456%2Cimgsize-11180.cms%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Fworld%2Feurope%2Fukrainian-drone-jammed-over-moscow-russias-defence-ministry%2Farticleshow%2F102642472.cms%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22%3Cimg%20border%3D%5C%220%5C%22%20align%3D%5C%22left%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Fphoto%2F102642472.cms%5C%22%20hspace%3D%5C%2210%5C%22%3E%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimeso