2%80%98on%E2%80%99%2C%20%E2%80%98behind%E2%80%99%2C%20or%20%E2%80%98beside%E2%80%99%2C%20are%20called%20prepositions.%20So%2C%20they%20easily%20understand%20the%20concept.%20Similarly%2C%20we%20teach%20other%20grammar%20concepts.%20This%20helps%20engage%20all%20the%20students%20and%20we%20see%20a%20great%20improvement%20in%20oral%20as%20well%20as%20writing%20skills%20of%20students.%20This%20kind%20of%20training%20is%20not%20happening%20anywhere%2C%E2%80%9D%20she%20adds.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EFor%20this%2C%20Rennis%20charges%20up%20to%20Rs%20700%20per%20student%20per%20year%20from%20low-cost%20private%20schools.%20For%20government%20schools%2C%20they%20do%20not%20charge%20any%20amount%20and%20manage%20expenses%20through%20CSR%20donations.%20But%20there%20have%20been%20times%20when%20he%20had%20to%20borrow%20from%20his%20friends%20to%20run%20the%20startup.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-image%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%201200px)%20100vw%2C%201200px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F08%2Fignis-careers-4-1691584816.jpg%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%221200%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Rennis%20and%20Imma%20started%20Ignis%20Careers%20in%202014.%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F08%2Fignis-careers-4-1691584816.jpg%201200w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F08%2Fignis-careers-4-1691584816-300x157.jpg%20300w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F08%2Fignis-careers-4-1691584816-500x262.jpg%20500w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F08%2Fignis-careers-4-1691584816-768x402.jpg%20768w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F08%2Fignis-careers-4-1691584816-150x79.jpg%20150w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-326824%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22628%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%20class%3D%5C%22wp-element-caption%5C%22%3ERennis%20and%20Imma%20started%20Ignis