%20the%20correct%20measures%20to%20take%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20adds.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESai%E2%80%99s%20inbox%20and%20phone%20are%20always%20buzzing%20with%20requests%20from%20people%20all%20around%20the%20city%20as%20well%20as%20the%20outskirts.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CThree%20years%20ago%2C%20we%20found%20a%20cow%20that%20had%20met%20with%20an%20accident%20and%20injured%20its%20leg.%20It%20was%20in%20deep%20pain%20and%20needed%20immediate%20attention.%20I%20had%20seen%20many%20of%20Sai%E2%80%99s%20reels%20on%20Instagram%20and%20was%20aware%20of%20his%20work.%20So%20I%20called%20for%20his%20help%2C%20and%20he%20rescued%20the%20cow%20and%20took%20it%20to%20his%20sanctuary%2C%E2%80%9D%20says%20Kathir%20Selvan%20who%20has%20been%20in%20touch%20with%20Sai%20ever%20since.%20He%20now%20informs%20Sai%20of%20any%20animal%20in%20distress%20that%20he%20happens%20to%20encounter.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-image%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%201200px)%20100vw%2C%201200px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F08%2Fsai--1691586928.jpg%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%221200%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Sai%20conducts%20sensitization%20seminars%20with%20the%20police%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F08%2Fsai--1691586928.jpg%201200w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F08%2Fsai--1691586928-300x157.jpg%20300w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F08%2Fsai--1691586928-500x262.jpg%20500w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F08%2Fsai--1691586928-768x402.jpg%20768w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F08%2Fsai--1691586928-150x79.jpg%20150w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-326852%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22628%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%20class%3D%5C%22wp-element-caption%5C%22%3ESai%20also%20conducts%20seminars%20for%20the%20sensitisation%20of%20police%20officers%20towards%20animal%20cruelty%3B%20Picture%20credit%3A%20Sai%20Vignesh%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ETalking%20about%20his%20motivations%20and%20reflecting%20on%20his%20journey%2C%20Sai%20says%2C%20%E2%80%9CWhen%20I%20see%20an%20animal%20in%20pain%2C%20it%20almost%20feels%20like%20I%20am%20experiencing%20it%20myself.%20They%20deserve%20to%20live%20as%20much%20as%20we%20do.%20There%20are%20days%20when%20the%20sanctuary%20is%20low%20on%20budget%20and%20hands%2C%20but%20we%20have%20somehow%20survived%20for%20all%20these%20years.%20At%20the%20end%20of%20the%20day%2C%20when%20I%20look%20back%20and%20see%20nature%20thriving%20in%20all%20its%20glory%20at%20the%20sanctuary%2C%20it%20fills%20me%20with%20indescribable%20joy%20and%20satisfaction.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3EHow%20you%20can%20help%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESai%2C%20who%20also%20works%20as%20a%20web%20developer%2C%20dedicates%20most%20of%20his%20income%20to%20the%20upkeep%20of%20the%20sanctuary.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CBesides%20my%20income%2C%20there%20are%20people%20who%20keep%20donating%20regularly%20in%20kind%20and%20money.%20The%20per-day%20expense%20for%20the%20sanctuary%E2%80%99s%20upkeep%20and%20for%20feeding%20the%20animals%20comes%20to%20around%20Rs%2018%2C000%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20shares.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CAnyone%20who%20wants%20to%20contribute%20can%20do%20it%20in%20any%20form.%20You%20can%20volunteer%20here%20as%20we%20are%20always%20short%20of%20hands%2C%20or%20you%20can%20also%20donate%20money%2C%20food%2C%20or%20medicines%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20says%2C%20adding%20that%20he%20regularly%20shares%20updates%20on%20the%20animals%E2%80%99%20health%20and%20well-being%20on%20social%20media.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ECurrently%2C%20Sai%20is%20planning%20to%20build%20a%20quarantine%20centre%20in%20the%20sanctuary%20for%20animals%20with%20contagious%20diseases.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3EIf%20you%20wish%20to%20further%20his%20cause%2C%20you%20c